- All-src files (.cpp , .txt & .ui):-

1] Admin.cpp
```
#include "Admin.h"
#include <iostream>

using namespace std;

void Admin::approveDonor(DatabaseManager& db, string phone) {
    string query = "UPDATE Donor SET approvalStatus = 1, available = 1 WHERE phone = '" + phone + "'";
    if (db.executeQuery(query))
        cout << "‚úÖ Donor approved successfully!\n";
}

void Admin::rejectDonor(DatabaseManager& db, string phone) {
    string query = "DELETE FROM Donor WHERE phone = '" + phone + "'";
    if (db.executeQuery(query))
        cout << "üö´ Donor rejected and removed from records.\n";
}

void Admin::removeInactiveDonor(DatabaseManager& db) {
    string query = "DELETE FROM Donor WHERE available = 0 AND approvalStatus = 1";
    if (db.executeQuery(query))
        cout << "üßπ Inactive donors removed successfully.\n";
}
```
2] AdminDialog.cpp
```
#include "AdminDialog.h"
#include "ui_AdminDialog.h"
#include <QMessageBox>
#include <QFileInfo>
#include <QDesktopServices>
#include <QUrl>

AdminDialog::AdminDialog(DatabaseManager *database, QWidget *parent) :
    QDialog(parent),
    ui(new Ui::AdminDialog),
    db(database) {
    
    ui->setupUi(this);
    setWindowTitle("Admin - Donor Approval");
    resize(1200, 700);
    
    // ‚úÖ DARK GRAY THEME - MATCHING DONOR REGISTRATION
    setStyleSheet(
        "QDialog {"

        "}"
    );
    
    // Setup table with proper column sizing
    ui->tablePending->setColumnCount(9);
    ui->tablePending->setHorizontalHeaderLabels({
        "Phone", "Name", "Age", "Gender", "Blood Group",
        "City", "Eligible", "Last Donation", "Health Report"
    });
    
    // Set column resize modes for proper alignment
    ui->tablePending->horizontalHeader()->setSectionResizeMode(QHeaderView::ResizeToContents);
    ui->tablePending->horizontalHeader()->setSectionResizeMode(1, QHeaderView::Stretch);  // Name column stretches
    ui->tablePending->horizontalHeader()->setStretchLastSection(false);
    
    // Enable word wrap for better text display
    ui->tablePending->setWordWrap(true);
    ui->tablePending->verticalHeader()->setDefaultSectionSize(40);  // Minimum row height
    ui->tablePending->setEditTriggers(QAbstractItemView::NoEditTriggers);
    ui->tablePending->setSelectionBehavior(QAbstractItemView::SelectRows);
    ui->tablePending->setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);
    
    // Connect signals
    connect(ui->btnLoadPending, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &AdminDialog::onLoadPendingClicked);
    connect(ui->btnApprove, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &AdminDialog::onApproveClicked);
    connect(ui->btnReject, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &AdminDialog::onRejectClicked);
    connect(ui->btnClose, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &AdminDialog::onCloseClicked);
    
    // Double-click to open health report
    connect(ui->tablePending, &QTableWidget::cellDoubleClicked,
            this, &AdminDialog::onTableCellDoubleClicked);
    
    // Auto-load on open
    loadPendingDonors();
}

AdminDialog::~AdminDialog() {
    delete ui;
}

void AdminDialog::loadPendingDonors() {
    QString query = "SELECT phone, name, age, gender, bloodGroup, city, eligibilityStatus, "
                    "lastDonationDate, healthReportPath "
                    "FROM Donor WHERE approvalStatus = 0 ORDER BY registrationDate DESC";
    
    auto results = db->fetchResults(query.toStdString());
    
    ui->tablePending->setRowCount(0);
    ui->tablePending->setColumnCount(9);
    ui->tablePending->setHorizontalHeaderLabels({
        "Phone", "Name", "Age", "Gender", "Blood Group",
        "City", "Eligible", "Last Donation", "Health Report"
    });
    
    for (size_t i = 0; i < results.size(); ++i) {
        ui->tablePending->insertRow(i);
        
        for (size_t j = 0; j < results[i].size(); ++j) {
            QString value = QString::fromStdString(results[i][j]);
            
            // Format eligible status
            if (j == 6) {
                value = (value == "1") ? "‚úÖ Yes" : "‚ùå No";
            }
            
            // Format last donation date
            if (j == 7) {
                if (value.isEmpty() || value == "0000-00-00") {
                    value = "NULL";
                }
            }
            
            // Format health report path - show only filename with clickable hint
            if (j == 8) {
                if (!value.isEmpty() && value != "NULL") {
                    QFileInfo fileInfo(value);
                    if (fileInfo.exists()) {
                        value = "üìÑ " + fileInfo.fileName();
                    } else {
                        value = "‚ùå Not uploaded";
                    }
                } else {
                    value = "‚ùå Not uploaded";
                }
            }
            
            QTableWidgetItem *item = new QTableWidgetItem(value);
            item->setTextAlignment(Qt::AlignCenter);
            
            // Store full path in the health report cell for later access
            if (j == 8 && !results[i][j].empty() && results[i][j] != "NULL") {
                item->setData(Qt::UserRole, QString::fromStdString(results[i][j]));
                item->setToolTip("Double-click to open health report");
                item->setForeground(QBrush(QColor(139, 63, 245)));  // Purple color for clickable
            }
            
            ui->tablePending->setItem(i, j, item);
        }
    }
    
    // Set specific widths for columns that should be compact
    ui->tablePending->setColumnWidth(0, 100);   // Phone
    ui->tablePending->setColumnWidth(2, 50);    // Age
    ui->tablePending->setColumnWidth(3, 80);    // Gender
    ui->tablePending->setColumnWidth(4, 100);   // Blood Group
    ui->tablePending->setColumnWidth(5, 100);   // City
    ui->tablePending->setColumnWidth(6, 80);    // Eligible
    ui->tablePending->setColumnWidth(7, 110);   // Last Donation
    ui->tablePending->setColumnWidth(8, 180);   // Health Report
    
    // Name column (index 1) will stretch to fill remaining space
    ui->tablePending->horizontalHeader()->setSectionResizeMode(1, QHeaderView::Stretch);
    
    // Adjust row heights to content
    ui->tablePending->resizeRowsToContents();
    
    ui->lblStatus->setText(QString("üìã Found %1 pending donor(s) - Double-click Health Report to view").arg(results.size()));
}

void AdminDialog::openHealthReport(const QString& filePath) {
    if (filePath.isEmpty() || filePath == "NULL") {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "No Report", "No health report uploaded for this donor.");
        return;
    }
    
    QFileInfo fileInfo(filePath);
    if (!fileInfo.exists()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "File Not Found",
            QString("Health report file not found:\n%1\n\n"
                    "The file may have been moved or deleted.").arg(filePath));
        return;
    }
    
    // Open file with default system application
    bool opened = QDesktopServices::openUrl(QUrl::fromLocalFile(filePath));
    
    if (!opened) {
        QMessageBox::critical(this, "Error Opening File",
            QString("Failed to open health report:\n%1\n\n"
                    "Please check if you have a program installed to open %2 files.")
            .arg(filePath)
            .arg(fileInfo.suffix().toUpper()));
    }
}

void AdminDialog::onTableCellDoubleClicked(int row, int column) {
    // Column 8 is the Health Report column
    if (column == 8) {
        QTableWidgetItem *item = ui->tablePending->item(row, column);
        if (item) {
            QString filePath = item->data(Qt::UserRole).toString();
            if (!filePath.isEmpty()) {
                QString donorName = ui->tablePending->item(row, 1)->text();
                auto reply = QMessageBox::question(this, "Open Health Report",
                    QString("Open health report for:\n%1\n\nFile: %2")
                    .arg(donorName)
                    .arg(QFileInfo(filePath).fileName()),
                    QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
                    
                if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
                    openHealthReport(filePath);
                }
            } else {
                QMessageBox::information(this, "No Report",
                    "No health report available for this donor.");
            }
        }
    }
}

void AdminDialog::onLoadPendingClicked() {
    loadPendingDonors();
    QMessageBox::information(this, "Refreshed", "Pending donors list has been refreshed.");
}

void AdminDialog::onApproveClicked() {
    int currentRow = ui->tablePending->currentRow();
    if (currentRow < 0) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "No Selection", "Please select a donor to approve.");
        return;
    }
    
    // Check eligibility before approving
    QString eligibleStatus = ui->tablePending->item(currentRow, 6)->text();
    if (eligibleStatus.contains("No") || eligibleStatus.contains("‚ùå")) {
        auto reply = QMessageBox::question(this, "Not Eligible",
            "‚ö†Ô∏è This donor is marked as NOT ELIGIBLE.\n\n"
            "Are you sure you want to approve?",
            QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
            
        if (reply == QMessageBox::No) {
            return;
        }
    }
    
    QString phone = ui->tablePending->item(currentRow, 0)->text();
    QString name = ui->tablePending->item(currentRow, 1)->text();
    
    auto reply = QMessageBox::question(this, "Confirm Approval",
        QString("‚úÖ Approve donor: %1 (%2)?").arg(name).arg(phone),
        QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
        
    if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
        admin.approveDonor(*db, phone.toStdString());
        QMessageBox::information(this, "Success",
            QString("‚úÖ %1 has been approved successfully!\n\n"
                    "The donor can now login and donate blood.").arg(name));
        loadPendingDonors();
    }
}

void AdminDialog::onRejectClicked() {
    int currentRow = ui->tablePending->currentRow();
    if (currentRow < 0) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "No Selection", "Please select a donor to reject.");
        return;
    }
    
    QString phone = ui->tablePending->item(currentRow, 0)->text();
    QString name = ui->tablePending->item(currentRow, 1)->text();
    
    auto reply = QMessageBox::question(this, "Confirm Rejection",
        QString("‚ùå Reject and remove donor: %1 (%2)?\n\n"
                "‚ö†Ô∏è This action cannot be undone!\n"
                "The donor's health report will remain in the system.")
        .arg(name).arg(phone),
        QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
        
    if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
        admin.rejectDonor(*db, phone.toStdString());
        QMessageBox::information(this, "Rejected",
            QString("üö´ %1 has been rejected and removed from pending list.").arg(name));
        loadPendingDonors();
    }
}

void AdminDialog::onCloseClicked() {
    accept();
}
```

5] Analytics.cpp
```
#include "Analytics.h"

std::vector<std::vector<std::string>>
Analytics::showDemandByBloodGroup(DatabaseManager& db) {
    std::string q =
        "SELECT bloodGroup, COUNT(*) AS total_searches "
        "FROM SearchLog GROUP BY bloodGroup ORDER BY total_searches DESC";
    return db.fetchResults(q);
}

std::vector<std::vector<std::string>>
Analytics::showAreaWiseTrends(DatabaseManager& db) {
    std::string q =
        "SELECT area, bloodGroup, COUNT(*) AS cnt "
        "FROM SearchLog GROUP BY area, bloodGroup ORDER BY area ASC, cnt DESC";
    return db.fetchResults(q);
}
```

6] AnalyticsDialog.cpp
```
#include "AnalyticsDialog.h"
#include "ui_AnalyticsDialog.h"

AnalyticsDialog::AnalyticsDialog(DatabaseManager *database, QWidget *parent) :
    QDialog(parent),
    ui(new Ui::AnalyticsDialog),
    db(database)
{
    ui->setupUi(this);
    setWindowTitle("Analytics Dashboard");
    resize(800, 600);
    
    // Setup table
    ui->tableAnalytics->horizontalHeader()->setStretchLastSection(true);
    ui->tableAnalytics->setEditTriggers(QAbstractItemView::NoEditTriggers);
    ui->tableAnalytics->setSelectionBehavior(QAbstractItemView::SelectRows);
    
    connect(ui->btnShowDemand, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &AnalyticsDialog::onShowDemandClicked);
    connect(ui->btnShowAreaTrends, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &AnalyticsDialog::onShowAreaTrendsClicked);
    connect(ui->btnClose, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &AnalyticsDialog::onCloseClicked);
}

AnalyticsDialog::~AnalyticsDialog()
{
    delete ui;
}

void AnalyticsDialog::displayTable(const std::vector<std::vector<std::string>>& data, 
                                  const QStringList& headers)
{
    ui->tableAnalytics->clear();
    ui->tableAnalytics->setColumnCount(headers.size());
    ui->tableAnalytics->setHorizontalHeaderLabels(headers);
    ui->tableAnalytics->setRowCount(data.size());
    
    for (size_t i = 0; i < data.size(); ++i) {
        for (size_t j = 0; j < data[i].size() && j < static_cast<size_t>(headers.size()); ++j) {
            QTableWidgetItem *item = new QTableWidgetItem(QString::fromStdString(data[i][j]));
            item->setTextAlignment(Qt::AlignCenter);
            ui->tableAnalytics->setItem(i, j, item);
        }
    }
    
    ui->tableAnalytics->resizeColumnsToContents();
}

void AnalyticsDialog::onShowDemandClicked()
{
    auto results = Analytics::showDemandByBloodGroup(*db);
    
    if (results.empty()) {
        ui->lblStatus->setText("‚ùå No search log data available for analysis.");
        ui->tableAnalytics->setRowCount(0);
        return;
    }
    
    QStringList headers;
    headers << "Blood Group" << "Total Searches";
    displayTable(results, headers);
    
    ui->lblStatus->setText(QString("üìä Blood Group Demand Analysis - %1 blood group(s)").arg(results.size()));
}

void AnalyticsDialog::onShowAreaTrendsClicked()
{
    auto results = Analytics::showAreaWiseTrends(*db);
    
    if (results.empty()) {
        ui->lblStatus->setText("‚ùå No search log data available for analysis.");
        ui->tableAnalytics->setRowCount(0);
        return;
    }
    
    QStringList headers;
    headers << "Area" << "Blood Group" << "Search Count";
    displayTable(results, headers);
    
    ui->lblStatus->setText(QString("üìç Area-wise Trends Analysis - %1 record(s)").arg(results.size()));
}

void AnalyticsDialog::onCloseClicked()
{
    accept();
}
```

9] BloodRequest.cpp
```
#include "BloodRequest.h"
#include <iostream>

using namespace std;

bool BloodRequest::createRequest(DatabaseManager& db, int hospitalID, 
                                const string& hospitalName, 
                                const string& contactInfo, 
                                const string& bloodType, 
                                const string& urgency) {
    // FIXED: Changed bloodType to bloodGroup to match database column name
    string query = "INSERT INTO BloodRequest(hospitalID, hospitalName, contactInfo, bloodGroup, urgency, status, requestDate) VALUES(" +
                   to_string(hospitalID) + ", '" + hospitalName + "', '" + contactInfo + "', '" + bloodType + "', '" + urgency + "', 'Pending', CURRENT_DATE)";
    
    if (db.executeQuery(query)) {
        cout << "‚úÖ Blood request created successfully!\n";
        return true;
    } else {
        cout << "‚ùå Failed to create blood request.\n";
        return false;
    }
}

vector<vector<string>> BloodRequest::getPendingRequests(DatabaseManager& db) {
    // FIXED: Changed bloodType to bloodGroup
    string query = "SELECT requestID, hospitalName, contactInfo, bloodGroup, urgency, requestDate FROM BloodRequest WHERE status = 'Pending' ORDER BY requestDate DESC";
    return db.fetchResults(query);
}

vector<vector<string>> BloodRequest::getRequestsByBloodType(DatabaseManager& db, 
                                                            const string& bloodType) {
    // FIXED: Changed bloodType to bloodGroup in WHERE clause
    string query = "SELECT requestID, hospitalName, contactInfo, bloodGroup, urgency, requestDate FROM BloodRequest WHERE status = 'Pending' AND bloodGroup = '" + bloodType + "' ORDER BY requestDate DESC";
    return db.fetchResults(query);
}

bool BloodRequest::markRequestFulfilled(DatabaseManager& db, int requestID) {
    string query = "UPDATE BloodRequest SET status = 'Fulfilled' WHERE requestID = " + to_string(requestID);
    if (db.executeQuery(query)) {
        cout << "‚úÖ Request marked as fulfilled.\n";
        return true;
    }
    return false;
}

bool BloodRequest::deleteRequest(DatabaseManager& db, int requestID) {
    string query = "DELETE FROM BloodRequest WHERE requestID = " + to_string(requestID);
    if (db.executeQuery(query)) {
        cout << "‚úÖ Request deleted successfully.\n";
        return true;
    }
    return false;
}

vector<string> BloodRequest::getRequestDetails(DatabaseManager& db, int requestID) {
    // FIXED: Changed bloodType to bloodGroup
    string query = "SELECT requestID, hospitalName, contactInfo, bloodGroup, urgency, requestDate, status FROM BloodRequest WHERE requestID = " + to_string(requestID);
    auto results = db.fetchResults(query);
    if (!results.empty()) {
        return results[0];
    }
    return vector<string>();
}
```

10] BloodRequestDialog.cpp
```
#include "BloodRequestDialog.h"
#include "ui_BloodRequestDialog.h"
#include "BloodRequest.h"
#include "DonationRequest.h"
#include <QMessageBox>
#include <QInputDialog>
#include <QDialog>
#include <QVBoxLayout>
#include <QTableWidget>
#include <QHeaderView>
#include <QPushButton>

BloodRequestDialog::BloodRequestDialog(DatabaseManager *database, QWidget *parent) :
    QDialog(parent),
    ui(new Ui::BloodRequestDialog),
    db(database) {
    
    ui->setupUi(this);
    setWindowTitle("ü©∏ Blood Request Management");
    resize(1000, 700);
    
    ui->cmbBloodTypeRequest->addItems({"A+", "A-", "B+", "B-", "AB+", "AB-", "O+", "O-"});
    ui->cmbUrgency->addItems({"Normal", "Urgent", "Critical"});
    
    ui->tableRequests->setColumnCount(6);
    ui->tableRequests->setHorizontalHeaderLabels({"Request ID", "Hospital Name", "Contact Info", 
                                                  "Blood Type", "Urgency", "Request Date"});
    ui->tableRequests->horizontalHeader()->setStretchLastSection(true);
    ui->tableRequests->setEditTriggers(QAbstractItemView::NoEditTriggers);
    ui->tableRequests->setSelectionBehavior(QAbstractItemView::SelectRows);
    ui->tableRequests->setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);
    
    connect(ui->btnCreateRequest, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &BloodRequestDialog::onCreateRequestClicked);
    connect(ui->btnRefresh, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &BloodRequestDialog::onRefreshClicked);
    connect(ui->btnDelete, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &BloodRequestDialog::onDeleteClicked);
    connect(ui->btnViewResponses, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &BloodRequestDialog::onViewResponsesClicked);
    connect(ui->btnClose, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &BloodRequestDialog::onCloseClicked);
    connect(ui->tableRequests, &QTableWidget::cellDoubleClicked, this, &BloodRequestDialog::onTableCellDoubleClicked);
    
    loadPendingRequests();
}

BloodRequestDialog::~BloodRequestDialog() {
    delete ui;
}

void BloodRequestDialog::onCreateRequestClicked() {
    if (!validateInputs()) {
        return;
    }
    
    QString hospitalName = ui->txtHospitalName->text();
    QString contactInfo = ui->txtContactInfo->text();
    QString bloodType = ui->cmbBloodTypeRequest->currentText();
    QString urgency = ui->cmbUrgency->currentText();
    
    if (BloodRequest::createRequest(*db, 1, hospitalName.toStdString(), 
                                   contactInfo.toStdString(), bloodType.toStdString(), 
                                   urgency.toStdString())) {
        QMessageBox::information(this, "Success", "Blood request created successfully!");
        ui->txtHospitalName->clear();
        ui->txtContactInfo->clear();
        ui->cmbBloodTypeRequest->setCurrentIndex(0);
        ui->cmbUrgency->setCurrentIndex(0);
        loadPendingRequests();
    } else {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error", "Failed to create blood request!");
    }
}

void BloodRequestDialog::onRefreshClicked() {
    loadPendingRequests();
    QMessageBox::information(this, "Refreshed", "Request list updated!");
}

void BloodRequestDialog::onDeleteClicked() {
    int currentRow = ui->tableRequests->currentRow();
    if (currentRow < 0) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "No Selection", "Please select a request to delete!");
        return;
    }
    
    int requestID = ui->tableRequests->item(currentRow, 0)->text().toInt();
    
    QMessageBox::StandardButton reply = QMessageBox::question(this, "Confirm Delete", 
                                                              "Are you sure you want to delete this request?",
                                                              QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
    
    if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
        if (BloodRequest::deleteRequest(*db, requestID)) {
            QMessageBox::information(this, "Success", "Request deleted!");
            loadPendingRequests();
        } else {
            QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error", "Failed to delete request!");
        }
    }
}

void BloodRequestDialog::onViewResponsesClicked() {
    int currentRow = ui->tableRequests->currentRow();
    if (currentRow < 0) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "No Selection", "Please select a request to view responses!");
        return;
    }
    
    int requestID = ui->tableRequests->item(currentRow, 0)->text().toInt();
    showDonorResponsesDialog(requestID);
}

// NEW FUNCTION - Interactive dialog to manage donor responses
void BloodRequestDialog::showDonorResponsesDialog(int requestID) {
    auto responses = DonationRequest::getDonationResponsesByRequest(*db, requestID);
    
    if (responses.empty()) {
        QMessageBox::information(this, "No Responses", 
                                "No donors have responded to this request yet.");
        return;
    }
    
    // Create custom dialog for response management
    QDialog *responseDialog = new QDialog(this);
    responseDialog->setWindowTitle(QString("Manage Responses - Request #%1").arg(requestID));
    responseDialog->resize(900, 500);
    
    QVBoxLayout *layout = new QVBoxLayout(responseDialog);
    
    // Add info label
    QLabel *infoLabel = new QLabel(QString("üìã Total Responses: %1 | Select a donor to accept/reject/complete").arg(responses.size()));
    infoLabel->setStyleSheet("font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt; padding: 10px;");
    layout->addWidget(infoLabel);
    
    // Create table for responses
    QTableWidget *responseTable = new QTableWidget();
    responseTable->setColumnCount(8);
    responseTable->setHorizontalHeaderLabels({"Response ID", "Donor ID", "Name", "Phone", 
                                              "Email", "City", "Status", "Date"});
    responseTable->horizontalHeader()->setStretchLastSection(true);
    responseTable->setEditTriggers(QAbstractItemView::NoEditTriggers);
    responseTable->setSelectionBehavior(QAbstractItemView::SelectRows);
    responseTable->setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);
    
    // Populate table
    responseTable->setRowCount(responses.size());
    for (size_t i = 0; i < responses.size(); ++i) {
        for (size_t j = 0; j < responses[i].size(); ++j) {
            QTableWidgetItem *item = new QTableWidgetItem(QString::fromStdString(responses[i][j]));
            
            // Color code by status (column 6)
            if (j == 6) {
                QString status = QString::fromStdString(responses[i][j]);
                if (status == "Accepted") {
                    item->setBackground(QColor(200, 255, 200)); // Light green
                    item->setForeground(QColor(0, 100, 0));
                } else if (status == "Rejected") {
                    item->setBackground(QColor(255, 200, 200)); // Light red
                    item->setForeground(QColor(100, 0, 0));
                } else if (status == "Completed") {
                    item->setBackground(QColor(180, 180, 255)); // Light blue
                    item->setForeground(QColor(0, 0, 100));
                } else {
                    item->setBackground(QColor(255, 255, 200)); // Light yellow
                }
                QFont font = item->font();
                font.setBold(true);
                item->setFont(font);
            }
            
            responseTable->setItem(i, j, item);
        }
    }
    
    layout->addWidget(responseTable);
    
    // Action buttons
    QHBoxLayout *buttonLayout = new QHBoxLayout();
    
    QPushButton *btnAccept = new QPushButton("‚úÖ Accept");
    btnAccept->setStyleSheet("background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px;");
    btnAccept->setMinimumHeight(40);
    
    QPushButton *btnReject = new QPushButton("‚ùå Reject");
    btnReject->setStyleSheet("background-color: #f44336; color: white; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px;");
    btnReject->setMinimumHeight(40);
    
    QPushButton *btnComplete = new QPushButton("ü©∏ Mark Completed");
    btnComplete->setStyleSheet("background-color: #2196F3; color: white; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px;");
    btnComplete->setMinimumHeight(40);
    
    QPushButton *btnClose = new QPushButton("Close");
    btnClose->setStyleSheet("background-color: #9E9E9E; color: white; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px;");
    btnClose->setMinimumHeight(40);
    
    buttonLayout->addWidget(btnAccept);
    buttonLayout->addWidget(btnReject);
    buttonLayout->addWidget(btnComplete);
    buttonLayout->addStretch();
    buttonLayout->addWidget(btnClose);
    
    layout->addLayout(buttonLayout);
    
    // Connect button actions
    connect(btnAccept, &QPushButton::clicked, [responseTable, responseDialog, this]() {
        int currentRow = responseTable->currentRow();
        if (currentRow < 0) {
            QMessageBox::warning(responseDialog, "No Selection", "Please select a donor response!");
            return;
        }
        
        int responseID = responseTable->item(currentRow, 0)->text().toInt();
        QString donorName = responseTable->item(currentRow, 2)->text();
        QString donorPhone = responseTable->item(currentRow, 3)->text();
        
        QMessageBox::StandardButton reply = QMessageBox::question(responseDialog, "Accept Response",
            QString("Accept donation from:\n\nüë§ %1\nüì± %2\n\nThe donor will be notified.")
            .arg(donorName).arg(donorPhone),
            QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
        
        if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
            if (DonationRequest::updateResponseStatus(*db, responseID, "Accepted")) {
                QMessageBox::information(responseDialog, "Success", 
                    "‚úÖ Response accepted!\n\nPlease contact the donor to schedule donation.");
                responseDialog->accept();
            } else {
                QMessageBox::warning(responseDialog, "Error", "Failed to update response!");
            }
        }
    });
    
    connect(btnReject, &QPushButton::clicked, [responseTable, responseDialog, this]() {
        int currentRow = responseTable->currentRow();
        if (currentRow < 0) {
            QMessageBox::warning(responseDialog, "No Selection", "Please select a donor response!");
            return;
        }
        
        int responseID = responseTable->item(currentRow, 0)->text().toInt();
        QString donorName = responseTable->item(currentRow, 2)->text();
        
        QMessageBox::StandardButton reply = QMessageBox::question(responseDialog, "Reject Response",
            QString("Reject donation from %1?").arg(donorName),
            QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
        
        if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
            if (DonationRequest::updateResponseStatus(*db, responseID, "Rejected")) {
                QMessageBox::information(responseDialog, "Success", "Response rejected.");
                responseDialog->accept();
            } else {
                QMessageBox::warning(responseDialog, "Error", "Failed to update response!");
            }
        }
    });
    
    connect(btnComplete, &QPushButton::clicked, [responseTable, responseDialog, this]() {
        int currentRow = responseTable->currentRow();
        if (currentRow < 0) {
            QMessageBox::warning(responseDialog, "No Selection", "Please select a donor response!");
            return;
        }
        
        int responseID = responseTable->item(currentRow, 0)->text().toInt();
        int donorID = responseTable->item(currentRow, 1)->text().toInt();
        QString donorName = responseTable->item(currentRow, 2)->text();
        QString currentStatus = responseTable->item(currentRow, 6)->text();
        
        if (currentStatus != "Accepted") {
            QMessageBox::warning(responseDialog, "Cannot Complete", 
                "Please accept the response first before marking it as completed!");
            return;
        }
        
        QMessageBox::StandardButton reply = QMessageBox::question(responseDialog, "Complete Donation",
            QString("Mark donation as COMPLETED for %1?\n\n‚ö†Ô∏è This will:\n"
                   "‚Ä¢ Update donor's last donation date\n"
                   "‚Ä¢ Start 90-day cooldown period\n"
                   "‚Ä¢ Set response status to Completed").arg(donorName),
            QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
        
        if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
            if (DonationRequest::recordDonation(*db, donorID, responseID)) {
                QMessageBox::information(responseDialog, "Success", 
                    "‚úÖ Donation marked as completed!\n\n"
                    "‚Ä¢ Donor's last donation date updated\n"
                    "‚Ä¢ 90-day cooldown started\n"
                    "‚Ä¢ Thank you for saving a life!");
                responseDialog->accept();
            } else {
                QMessageBox::warning(responseDialog, "Error", "Failed to record donation!");
            }
        }
    });
    
    connect(btnClose, &QPushButton::clicked, responseDialog, &QDialog::accept);
    
    responseDialog->exec();
    delete responseDialog;
}

void BloodRequestDialog::onCloseClicked() {
    accept();
}

void BloodRequestDialog::onTableCellDoubleClicked(int row, int column) {
    Q_UNUSED(column);
    int requestID = ui->tableRequests->item(row, 0)->text().toInt();
    showDonorResponsesDialog(requestID);
}

void BloodRequestDialog::loadPendingRequests() {
    auto requests = BloodRequest::getPendingRequests(*db);
    displayRequests(requests);
}

void BloodRequestDialog::displayRequests(const std::vector<std::vector<std::string>>& requests) {
    ui->tableRequests->setRowCount(0);
    
    for (size_t i = 0; i < requests.size(); ++i) {
        ui->tableRequests->insertRow(i);
        
        for (size_t j = 0; j < requests[i].size(); ++j) {
            ui->tableRequests->setItem(i, j, new QTableWidgetItem(QString::fromStdString(requests[i][j])));
        }
    }
}

bool BloodRequestDialog::validateInputs() {
    if (ui->txtHospitalName->text().trimmed().isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter hospital name!");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (ui->txtContactInfo->text().trimmed().isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter contact information!");
        return false;
    }
    
    return true;
}
```

13] DatabaseManager.cpp
```
#include "DatabaseManager.h"

DatabaseManager::DatabaseManager() {
    conn = mysql_init(0);
    connected = false;
}

DatabaseManager::~DatabaseManager() {
    if (connected)
        closeConnection();
}

bool DatabaseManager::connectDB(string host, string user, string pass, string db, unsigned int port) {
    conn = mysql_real_connect(conn, host.c_str(), user.c_str(), pass.c_str(), db.c_str(), port, NULL, 0);
    if (conn) {
        connected = true;
        cout << "‚úÖ Connected to MySQL Database successfully!\n";
        return true;
    } else {
        cout << "‚ùå Connection failed: " << mysql_error(conn) << endl;
        return false;
    }
}

void DatabaseManager::closeConnection() {
    mysql_close(conn);
    connected = false;
    cout << "üîí Database connection closed.\n";
}

bool DatabaseManager::executeQuery(const string& query) {
    if (!connected) {
        cout << "‚ö†Ô∏è No active connection!\n";
        return false;
    }
    
    if (mysql_query(conn, query.c_str())) {
        cout << "‚ùå Query failed: " << mysql_error(conn) << endl;
        return false;
    }
    
    return true;
}

vector<vector<string>> DatabaseManager::fetchResults(const string& query) {
    vector<vector<string>> results;
    if (!connected) return results;
    
    if (mysql_query(conn, query.c_str())) {
        cout << "‚ùå Query failed: " << mysql_error(conn) << endl;
        return results;
    }
    
    res = mysql_store_result(conn);
    int fields = mysql_num_fields(res);
    
    while ((row = mysql_fetch_row(res))) {
        vector<string> r;
        for (int i = 0; i < fields; i++)
            r.push_back(row[i] ? row[i] : "NULL");
        results.push_back(r);
    }
    
    mysql_free_result(res);
    return results;
}

bool DatabaseManager::isConnected() const { 
    return connected; 
}
```

14] DonationRequest.cpp
```
#include "DonationRequest.h"
#include <iostream>

using namespace std;

bool DonationRequest::createDonationResponse(DatabaseManager& db, 
                                            int donorID, 
                                            int requestID, 
                                            const string& status) {
    string checkQuery = "SELECT COUNT(*) FROM DonationResponse WHERE donorID = " + 
                       to_string(donorID) + " AND requestID = " + to_string(requestID);
    auto checkResult = db.fetchResults(checkQuery);
    
    if (!checkResult.empty() && checkResult[0][0] != "0") {
        cout << "‚ö†Ô∏è You have already responded to this request.\n";
        return false;
    }
    
    string query = "INSERT INTO DonationResponse(donorID, requestID, status, responseDate) VALUES(" +
                   to_string(donorID) + ", " + to_string(requestID) + ", '" + status + "', CURRENT_DATE)";
    
    if (db.executeQuery(query)) {
        cout << "‚úÖ Your donation interest has been recorded!\n";
        return true;
    } else {
        cout << "‚ùå Failed to record response.\n";
        return false;
    }
}

vector<vector<string>> DonationRequest::getDonationResponsesByRequest(DatabaseManager& db, 
                                                                      int requestID) {
    string query = "SELECT dr.responseID, d.donorID, d.name, d.phone, d.email, d.city, dr.status, dr.responseDate FROM DonationResponse dr "
                   "JOIN Donor d ON dr.donorID = d.donorID WHERE dr.requestID = " + 
                   to_string(requestID) + " ORDER BY dr.responseDate DESC";
    return db.fetchResults(query);
}

vector<vector<string>> DonationRequest::getDonationResponsesByDonor(DatabaseManager& db, 
                                                                    int donorID) {
    // FIXED: Changed bloodType to bloodGroup
    string query = "SELECT dr.responseID, br.requestID, br.hospitalName, br.bloodGroup, br.urgency, dr.status, dr.responseDate FROM DonationResponse dr "
                   "JOIN BloodRequest br ON dr.requestID = br.requestID WHERE dr.donorID = " + 
                   to_string(donorID) + " ORDER BY dr.responseDate DESC";
    return db.fetchResults(query);
}

bool DonationRequest::updateResponseStatus(DatabaseManager& db, int responseID, 
                                          const string& status) {
    string query = "UPDATE DonationResponse SET status = '" + status + "' WHERE responseID = " + 
                   to_string(responseID);
    
    if (db.executeQuery(query)) {
        cout << "‚úÖ Response status updated.\n";
        return true;
    }
    return false;
}

bool DonationRequest::isDonorEligibleToDonate(DatabaseManager& db, int donorID) {
    string query = "SELECT lastDonationDate FROM Donor WHERE donorID = " + to_string(donorID);
    auto results = db.fetchResults(query);
    
    if (results.empty()) {
        return false;
    }
    
    string lastDonationStr = results[0][0];
    
    if (lastDonationStr.empty() || lastDonationStr == "NULL" || lastDonationStr == "0000-00-00") {
        return true;
    }
    
    int daysSince = daysSinceLastDonation(db, donorID);
    
    if (daysSince >= 90) {
        return true;
    }
    
    return false;
}

string DonationRequest::getLastDonationDate(DatabaseManager& db, int donorID) {
    string query = "SELECT lastDonationDate FROM Donor WHERE donorID = " + to_string(donorID);
    auto results = db.fetchResults(query);
    
    if (!results.empty() && !results[0][0].empty()) {
        return results[0][0];
    }
    return "Never";
}

int DonationRequest::daysSinceLastDonation(DatabaseManager& db, int donorID) {
    string query = "SELECT DATEDIFF(CURDATE(), lastDonationDate) as days FROM Donor WHERE donorID = " + 
                   to_string(donorID);
    auto results = db.fetchResults(query);
    
    if (!results.empty() && !results[0][0].empty()) {
        try {
            int days = stoi(results[0][0]);
            return (days < 0) ? 0 : days;
        } catch (...) {
            return 0;
        }
    }
    return 999;
}

bool DonationRequest::recordDonation(DatabaseManager& db, int donorID, int responseID) {
    string query = "UPDATE Donor SET lastDonationDate = CURDATE() WHERE donorID = " + 
                   to_string(donorID);
    
    if (db.executeQuery(query)) {
        string updateResponse = "UPDATE DonationResponse SET status = 'Completed' WHERE responseID = " + 
                               to_string(responseID);
        db.executeQuery(updateResponse);
        
        cout << "‚úÖ Donation recorded successfully! Next eligible after 90 days.\n";
        return true;
    }
    return false;
}
```

15] Donor.cpp
```
#include "Donor.h"
#include <iostream>

using namespace std;

Donor::Donor() {
    available = healthTestStatus = eligibilityStatus = approvalStatus = false;
}

bool Donor::checkEligibility() {
    return (age >= 18 && age <= 65 && healthTestStatus);
}

void Donor::registerDonor(DatabaseManager& db) {
    cout << "Enter Name: "; getline(cin, name);
    cout << "Enter Age: "; cin >> age; cin.ignore();
    cout << "Enter Gender: "; getline(cin, gender);
    cout << "Enter Phone: "; getline(cin, phone);
    cout << "Enter City: "; getline(cin, city);
    cout << "Enter Address: "; getline(cin, address);
    cout << "Enter Blood Group: "; getline(cin, bloodGroup);
    cout << "Have you passed health test (1/0): "; cin >> healthTestStatus;
    
    eligibilityStatus = checkEligibility();
    approvalStatus = false;
    
    string query = "INSERT INTO Donor(name, age, gender, phone, city, address, bloodGroup, available, healthTestStatus, eligibilityStatus, approvalStatus) VALUES('" +
                   name + "', " + to_string(age) + ", '" + gender + "', '" + phone + "', '" + 
                   city + "', '" + address + "', '" + bloodGroup + "', 0, " + 
                   to_string(healthTestStatus) + ", " + to_string(eligibilityStatus) + ", 0)";
    
    if (db.executeQuery(query))
        cout << "‚úÖ Registration submitted! Awaiting admin approval.\n";
    else
        cout << "‚ùå Registration failed.\n";
}

void Donor::updateAvailability(DatabaseManager& db, bool newStatus) {
    available = newStatus;
    string query = "UPDATE Donor SET available = " + to_string(available) + " WHERE phone = '" + phone + "'";
    if (db.executeQuery(query))
        cout << "‚úÖ Availability updated!\n";
}

void Donor::showDonationHistory(DatabaseManager& db) {
    cout << "üìú Donation history feature coming soon.\n";
}
```

16] DonorDashboard.cpp
```
#include "DonorDashboard.h"
#include "ui_DonorDashboard.h"
#include <QMessageBox>
#include <QInputDialog>

DonorDashboard::DonorDashboard(DatabaseManager *database, int donorID, const QString& donorName, QWidget *parent) :
    QDialog(parent),
    ui(new Ui::DonorDashboard),
    db(database),
    currentDonorID(donorID),
    currentDonorName(donorName)
{
    ui->setupUi(this);
    setWindowTitle("Donor Dashboard");
    resize(700, 500);

    loadDonorInfo();

    // Connect signals
    connect(ui->toggleAvailability, &QCheckBox::toggled, this, &DonorDashboard::onAvailabilityToggled);
    connect(ui->btnEditProfile, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &DonorDashboard::onEditProfileClicked);
    connect(ui->btnViewHistory, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &DonorDashboard::onViewHistoryClicked);
    connect(ui->btnClose, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &DonorDashboard::onCloseClicked);
}

DonorDashboard::~DonorDashboard()
{
    delete ui;
}

void DonorDashboard::loadDonorInfo()
{
    QString query = QString(
        "SELECT name, age, gender, phone, email, city, bloodGroup, available, lastDonationDate "
        "FROM Donor WHERE donorID = %1").arg(currentDonorID);

    auto results = db->fetchResults(query.toStdString());

    if (!results.empty()) {
        ui->lblWelcome->setText(QString("Welcome, %1!").arg(QString::fromStdString(results[0][0])));
        
        QString info = QString(
            "üìå Personal Information\n\n"
            "Name: %1\n"
            "Age: %2\n"
            "Gender: %3\n"
            "Phone: %4\n"
            "Email: %5\n"
            "City: %6\n"
            "Blood Group: %7\n"
            "Last Donation: %8")
            .arg(QString::fromStdString(results[0][0]))
            .arg(QString::fromStdString(results[0][1]))
            .arg(QString::fromStdString(results[0][2]))
            .arg(QString::fromStdString(results[0][3]))
            .arg(QString::fromStdString(results[0][4]))
            .arg(QString::fromStdString(results[0][5]))
            .arg(QString::fromStdString(results[0][6]))
            .arg(results[0][8].empty() ? "Never" : QString::fromStdString(results[0][8]));

        ui->txtDonorInfo->setPlainText(info);

        // Set availability toggle
        bool available = (results[0][7] == "1");
        ui->toggleAvailability->blockSignals(true);
        ui->toggleAvailability->setChecked(available);
        ui->toggleAvailability->blockSignals(false);
        
        if (available) {
            ui->lblAvailabilityStatus->setText("‚úÖ You are available for donation in your city");
            ui->lblAvailabilityStatus->setStyleSheet("color: green; font-weight: bold;");
        } else {
            ui->lblAvailabilityStatus->setText("‚ùå You are currently unavailable (Out of city or unavailable)");
            ui->lblAvailabilityStatus->setStyleSheet("color: red; font-weight: bold;");
        }
    }
}

void DonorDashboard::updateAvailabilityInDB(bool available)
{
    QString query = QString("UPDATE Donor SET available = %1 WHERE donorID = %2")
                        .arg(available ? 1 : 0)
                        .arg(currentDonorID);

    if (db->executeQuery(query.toStdString())) {
        if (available) {
            ui->lblAvailabilityStatus->setText("‚úÖ You are available for donation in your city");
            ui->lblAvailabilityStatus->setStyleSheet("color: green; font-weight: bold;");
            QMessageBox::information(this, "Availability Updated", 
                "‚úÖ Your availability status is now ON.\n\n"
                "Hospitals can now find you for blood donation requests.");
        } else {
            ui->lblAvailabilityStatus->setText("‚ùå You are currently unavailable (Out of city or unavailable)");
            ui->lblAvailabilityStatus->setStyleSheet("color: red; font-weight: bold;");
            QMessageBox::information(this, "Availability Updated", 
                "‚ùå Your availability status is now OFF.\n\n"
                "You will not appear in hospital searches.");
        }
    }
}

void DonorDashboard::onAvailabilityToggled(bool checked)
{
    QString message;
    if (checked) {
        message = "‚úÖ Turn ON your availability?\n\n"
                  "This means you are currently in your registered city "
                  "and available to donate blood if needed.";
    } else {
        message = "‚ùå Turn OFF your availability?\n\n"
                  "Use this when you're out of city or unable to donate.";
    }

    auto reply = QMessageBox::question(this, "Confirm Availability Change", 
                                       message,
                                       QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);

    if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
        updateAvailabilityInDB(checked);
    } else {
        // Revert the toggle
        ui->toggleAvailability->blockSignals(true);
        ui->toggleAvailability->setChecked(!checked);
        ui->toggleAvailability->blockSignals(false);
    }
}

void DonorDashboard::onEditProfileClicked()
{
    // Create a menu to choose what to edit
    QMessageBox msgBox;
    msgBox.setWindowTitle("Edit Profile");
    msgBox.setText("What would you like to update?");
    
    QPushButton *emailBtn = msgBox.addButton("Update Email", QMessageBox::ActionRole);
    QPushButton *cityBtn = msgBox.addButton("Update City", QMessageBox::ActionRole);
    QPushButton *addressBtn = msgBox.addButton("Update Address", QMessageBox::ActionRole);
    QPushButton *cancelBtn = msgBox.addButton("Cancel", QMessageBox::RejectRole);
    
    msgBox.exec();
    
    if (msgBox.clickedButton() == emailBtn) {
        // Update Email
        bool ok;
        QString newEmail = QInputDialog::getText(this, "Update Email",
                                                 "Enter new email address:",
                                                 QLineEdit::Normal,
                                                 "", &ok);
        if (ok && !newEmail.isEmpty()) {
            QString query = QString("UPDATE Donor SET email = '%1' WHERE donorID = %2")
                                .arg(newEmail).arg(currentDonorID);
            if (db->executeQuery(query.toStdString())) {
                QMessageBox::information(this, "Success", "‚úÖ Email updated successfully!");
                loadDonorInfo();
            }
        }
    }
    else if (msgBox.clickedButton() == cityBtn) {
        // Update City
        bool ok;
        QString newCity = QInputDialog::getText(this, "Update City",
                                                "Enter new city:",
                                                QLineEdit::Normal,
                                                "", &ok);
        if (ok && !newCity.isEmpty()) {
            auto reply = QMessageBox::question(this, "Confirm City Change",
                QString("Change your city to: %1?\n\n"
                        "Your availability will be set to OFF.\n"
                        "You can turn it ON once you're settled.").arg(newCity),
                QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
            
            if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
                QString query = QString("UPDATE Donor SET city = '%1', available = 0 WHERE donorID = %2")
                                    .arg(newCity).arg(currentDonorID);
                if (db->executeQuery(query.toStdString())) {
                    QMessageBox::information(this, "Success", 
                        "‚úÖ City updated successfully!\n"
                        "‚ö†Ô∏è Your availability has been set to OFF.");
                    loadDonorInfo();
                }
            }
        }
    }
    else if (msgBox.clickedButton() == addressBtn) {
        // Update Address
        bool ok;
        QString newAddress = QInputDialog::getMultiLineText(this, "Update Address",
                                                            "Enter new address:",
                                                            "", &ok);
        if (ok && !newAddress.isEmpty()) {
            QString query = QString("UPDATE Donor SET address = '%1' WHERE donorID = %2")
                                .arg(newAddress).arg(currentDonorID);
            if (db->executeQuery(query.toStdString())) {
                QMessageBox::information(this, "Success", "‚úÖ Address updated successfully!");
                loadDonorInfo();
            }
        }
    }
}

void DonorDashboard::onViewHistoryClicked()
{
    QMessageBox::information(this, "Coming Soon", 
        "üìú Donation History\n\n"
        "This feature will show your complete donation history including:\n"
        "‚Ä¢ Donation dates\n"
        "‚Ä¢ Blood quantity donated\n"
        "‚Ä¢ Hospital details\n\n"
        "Coming soon in the next update!");
}

void DonorDashboard::onCloseClicked()
{
    accept();
}
```

```
#include "DonorDialog.h"
#include "ui_DonorDialog.h"
#include <QMessageBox>
#include <QFileDialog>
#include <QFileInfo>
#include <QDir>
#include <QFile>


DonorDialog::DonorDialog(DatabaseManager *database, QWidget *parent) :
    QDialog(parent),
    ui(new Ui::DonorDialog),
    db(database) {
    
    ui->setupUi(this);
    setWindowTitle("Donor Registration");
    resize(650, 850);
    setMinimumSize(600, 800);
    
    // ‚úÖ DARK GRAY THEME - MATCHING YOUR SECOND IMAGE
    setStyleSheet(
        "QDialog {"
        "   background: #2B2D3E;"  // Dark gray background
        "}"
        "QWidget {"
        "   background: #2B2D3E;"
        "}"

        "   border: 1px solid #5A5D7A;"
        "   padding: 5px;"
        "   selection-background-color: #8B3FF5;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QWidget#qt_calendar_navigationbar {"
        "   background: #8B3FF5;"
        "   padding: 5px;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QWidget#qt_calendar_prevmonth,"
        "QCalendarWidget QWidget#qt_calendar_nextmonth {"
        "   background: transparent;"
        "   color: white;"
        "   border: none;"
        "   qproperty-icon: none;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QWidget#qt_calendar_prevmonth:hover,"
        "QCalendarWidget QWidget#qt_calendar_nextmonth:hover {"
        "   background: #9B4FFF;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QAbstractItemView:enabled {"
        "   background: #2B2D3E;"
        "   color: #FFFFFF;"
        "   selection-background-color: #8B3FF5;"
        "   selection-color: white;"
        "   border: none;"
        "   outline: none;"
        "   font-size: 14px;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QAbstractItemView:disabled {"
        "   color: #6A6C7E;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QTableView {"
        "   background: #2B2D3E;"
        "   color: #FFFFFF;"
        "   alternate-background-color: #32344A;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QHeaderView::section {"
        "   background: #8B3FF5;"
        "   color: white;"
        "   padding: 8px;"
        "   border: none;"
        "   font-weight: bold;"
        "   font-size: 12px;"
        "}"
    );
    
    // Setup blood group combo box
    ui->cmbBloodGroup->addItems({"A+", "A-", "B+", "B-", "AB+", "AB-", "O+", "O-"});
    
    // Setup gender combo box
    ui->cmbGender->addItems({"Male", "Female", "Other"});
    
    // Connect signals
    connect(ui->btnRegister, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &DonorDialog::onRegisterClicked);
    connect(ui->btnCancel, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &DonorDialog::onCancelClicked);
    connect(ui->btnBrowseHealthReport, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &DonorDialog::onBrowseHealthReportClicked);
}


DonorDialog::~DonorDialog() {
    delete ui;
}


bool DonorDialog::validateInputs() {
    if (ui->txtName->text().trimmed().isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter donor name.");
        return false;
    }
    
    QString phone = ui->txtPhone->text().trimmed();
    if (phone.length() != 10 || !phone.toULongLong()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter a valid 10-digit phone number.");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (ui->spinAge->value() < 18 || ui->spinAge->value() > 65) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Donor age must be between 18 and 65.");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (ui->txtCity->text().trimmed().isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter city.");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (ui->txtAddress->toPlainText().trimmed().isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter address.");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (!ui->chkHealthTest->isChecked()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error",
            "Please confirm that you have passed health test by checking the box.");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (healthReportFilePath.isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error",
            "Please upload your health report document.");
        return false;
    }
    
    return true;
}


void DonorDialog::onBrowseHealthReportClicked() {
    QString fileName = QFileDialog::getOpenFileName(this,
        "Select Health Report",
        QDir::homePath(),
        "Documents (*.pdf *.doc *.docx *.jpg *.jpeg *.png);;All Files (*)");
    
    if (!fileName.isEmpty()) {
        healthReportFilePath = fileName;
        QFileInfo fileInfo(fileName);
        ui->lblHealthReportStatus->setText(QString("‚úÖ Selected: %1").arg(fileInfo.fileName()));
        ui->lblHealthReportStatus->setStyleSheet("color: #1ABC9C; font-weight: bold;");
    }
}


void DonorDialog::onRegisterClicked() {
    if (!validateInputs()) {
        return;
    }
    
    QString name = ui->txtName->text().trimmed();
    int age = ui->spinAge->value();
    QString gender = ui->cmbGender->currentText();
    QString phone = ui->txtPhone->text().trimmed();
    QString city = ui->txtCity->text().trimmed();
    QString address = ui->txtAddress->toPlainText().trimmed();
    QString bloodGroup = ui->cmbBloodGroup->currentText();
    bool healthTestStatus = ui->chkHealthTest->isChecked();
    QString lastDonationDate = ui->dateLastDonation->date().toString("yyyy-MM-dd");
    
    bool eligible = (age >= 18 && age <= 65 && healthTestStatus);
    
    QString checkQuery = QString("SELECT phone FROM Donor WHERE phone = '%1'").arg(phone);
    auto existing = db->fetchResults(checkQuery.toStdString());
    if (!existing.empty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Registration Failed",
            "This phone number is already registered!");
        return;
    }
    
    QString appDataPath = QDir::currentPath() + "/health_reports";
    QDir dir;
    if (!dir.exists(appDataPath)) {
        dir.mkpath(appDataPath);
    }
    
    QFileInfo fileInfo(healthReportFilePath);
    QString newFileName = QString("%1_%2").arg(phone).arg(fileInfo.fileName());
    QString destinationPath = appDataPath + "/" + newFileName;
    
    if (QFile::exists(destinationPath)) {
        QFile::remove(destinationPath);
    }
    
    if (!QFile::copy(healthReportFilePath, destinationPath)) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "File Error",
            "Failed to save health report. Please try again.");
        return;
    }
    
    QString query = QString(
        "INSERT INTO Donor(name, age, gender, phone, city, address, bloodGroup, "
        "available, healthTestStatus, eligibilityStatus, approvalStatus, lastDonationDate, healthReportPath) "
        "VALUES('%1', %2, '%3', '%4', '%5', '%6', '%7', 0, %8, %9, 0, '%10', '%11')")
        .arg(name).arg(age).arg(gender).arg(phone).arg(city).arg(address).arg(bloodGroup)
        .arg(healthTestStatus ? 1 : 0)
        .arg(eligible ? 1 : 0)
        .arg(lastDonationDate)
        .arg(destinationPath);
    
    if (db->executeQuery(query.toStdString())) {
        QMessageBox::information(this, "Success",
            "‚úÖ Donor registration submitted successfully!\n\n"
            "üìã Your application is pending admin approval.\n"
            "üìÑ Health report uploaded successfully.\n"
            "üìÖ Last donation date recorded.\n\n"
            "You will be notified once approved.");
        accept();
    } else {
        QMessageBox::critical(this, "Error",
            "Registration failed. Please try again.");
    }
}


void DonorDialog::onCancelClicked() {
    reject();
}
```

22] DonorRequestsBoard.cpp
```
#include "DonorRequestsBoard.h"
#include "ui_DonorRequestsBoard.h"
#include "BloodRequest.h"
#include "DonationRequest.h"
#include <QMessageBox>

DonorRequestsBoard::DonorRequestsBoard(DatabaseManager *database, int donorID, 
                                       const QString& donorName, QWidget *parent) :
    QDialog(parent),
    ui(new Ui::DonorRequestsBoard),
    db(database),
    currentDonorID(donorID),
    currentDonorName(donorName) {
    
    ui->setupUi(this);
    setWindowTitle("ü©∏ Blood Donation Requests");
    resize(1000, 700);
    
    ui->tableBloodRequests->setColumnCount(6);
    ui->tableBloodRequests->setHorizontalHeaderLabels({"Request ID", "Hospital Name", "Contact Info", 
                                                       "Blood Type", "Urgency", "Request Date"});
    ui->tableBloodRequests->horizontalHeader()->setStretchLastSection(true);
    ui->tableBloodRequests->setEditTriggers(QAbstractItemView::NoEditTriggers);
    ui->tableBloodRequests->setSelectionBehavior(QAbstractItemView::SelectRows);
    ui->tableBloodRequests->setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);
    
    connect(ui->btnRefresh, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &DonorRequestsBoard::onRefreshClicked);
    connect(ui->btnRespondToRequest, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &DonorRequestsBoard::onRespondToRequestClicked);
    connect(ui->btnViewMyResponses, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &DonorRequestsBoard::onViewMyResponsesClicked);
    connect(ui->btnClose, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &DonorRequestsBoard::onCloseClicked);
    connect(ui->tableBloodRequests, &QTableWidget::cellDoubleClicked, this, &DonorRequestsBoard::onTableCellDoubleClicked);
    
    // NEW - Load donor's blood group first
    loadDonorBloodGroup();
    checkDonorEligibility();
    loadAllRequests();
}

DonorRequestsBoard::~DonorRequestsBoard() {
    delete ui;
}

// NEW FUNCTION - Get donor's blood group from database
void DonorRequestsBoard::loadDonorBloodGroup() {
    QString query = QString("SELECT bloodGroup FROM Donor WHERE donorID = %1").arg(currentDonorID);
    auto results = db->fetchResults(query.toStdString());
    
    if (!results.empty() && !results[0].empty()) {
        donorBloodGroup = QString::fromStdString(results[0][0]);
        
        // Update title to show donor's blood group
        QString newTitle = QString("ü©∏ Blood Donation Requests - Your Blood Type: %1").arg(donorBloodGroup);
        setWindowTitle(newTitle);
    } else {
        donorBloodGroup = "";
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error", "Could not retrieve your blood group!");
    }
}

void DonorRequestsBoard::checkDonorEligibility() {
    bool eligible = DonationRequest::isDonorEligibleToDonate(*db, currentDonorID);
    
    if (eligible) {
        int daysSince = DonationRequest::daysSinceLastDonation(*db, currentDonorID);
        if (daysSince == 999) {
            ui->lblEligibilityStatus->setText(QString("‚úÖ Eligible to Donate (%1) - Never donated before").arg(donorBloodGroup));
            ui->lblEligibilityStatus->setStyleSheet("color: green; font-weight: bold;");
        } else {
            ui->lblEligibilityStatus->setText(QString("‚úÖ Eligible to Donate (%1) - Last donation %2 days ago").arg(donorBloodGroup).arg(daysSince));
            ui->lblEligibilityStatus->setStyleSheet("color: green; font-weight: bold;");
        }
        ui->btnRespondToRequest->setEnabled(true);
    } else {
        int daysSince = DonationRequest::daysSinceLastDonation(*db, currentDonorID);
        int daysRemaining = 90 - daysSince;
        QString lastDate = QString::fromStdString(DonationRequest::getLastDonationDate(*db, currentDonorID));
        
        ui->lblEligibilityStatus->setText(QString("‚ùå Not Eligible (%1) - Last Donation: %2 | %3 days remaining").arg(donorBloodGroup).arg(lastDate).arg(daysRemaining));
        ui->lblEligibilityStatus->setStyleSheet("color: red; font-weight: bold;");
        ui->btnRespondToRequest->setEnabled(false);
    }
}

void DonorRequestsBoard::onRefreshClicked() {
    checkDonorEligibility();
    loadAllRequests();
    QMessageBox::information(this, "Refreshed", "Request list updated!");
}

void DonorRequestsBoard::onRespondToRequestClicked() {
    int currentRow = ui->tableBloodRequests->currentRow();
    if (currentRow < 0) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "No Selection", "Please select a request to respond to!");
        return;
    }
    
    if (!isDonorEligible()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Not Eligible", "You are not eligible to donate at this time. Please wait for the cooldown period to end.");
        return;
    }
    
    int requestID = ui->tableBloodRequests->item(currentRow, 0)->text().toInt();
    QString bloodType = ui->tableBloodRequests->item(currentRow, 3)->text();
    QString hospitalName = ui->tableBloodRequests->item(currentRow, 1)->text();
    
    // VERIFICATION - Double-check blood type matches (should always match due to filtering)
    if (bloodType != donorBloodGroup) {
        QMessageBox::critical(this, "Error", 
            QString("Blood type mismatch!\nRequest is for: %1\nYour blood type: %2\n\nYou cannot respond to this request.")
            .arg(bloodType).arg(donorBloodGroup));
        return;
    }
    
    QMessageBox::StandardButton reply = QMessageBox::question(this, "Confirm Response", 
                                                              QString("Do you want to donate for:\nHospital: %1\nBlood Type: %2\n\nThis matches your blood type (%3)")
                                                              .arg(hospitalName).arg(bloodType).arg(donorBloodGroup),
                                                              QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
    
    if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
        if (DonationRequest::createDonationResponse(*db, currentDonorID, requestID, "Pending")) {
            QMessageBox::information(this, "Success", 
                QString("‚úÖ Your interest has been recorded!\n\nThe hospital will contact you soon at your registered phone number."));
            loadAllRequests();
        } else {
            QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error", "Failed to record your response! You may have already responded to this request.");
        }
    }
}

void DonorRequestsBoard::onViewMyResponsesClicked() {
    auto responses = DonationRequest::getDonationResponsesByDonor(*db, currentDonorID);
    
    if (responses.empty()) {
        QMessageBox::information(this, "My Responses", "You haven't responded to any requests yet!");
        return;
    }
    
    QString details = QString("Your Donation Responses (%1):\n\n").arg(donorBloodGroup);
    for (const auto& response : responses) {
        details += QString("Hospital: %1\nBlood Type: %2\nUrgency: %3\nStatus: %4\nDate: %5\n\n")
                  .arg(response[2].c_str())
                  .arg(response[3].c_str())
                  .arg(response[4].c_str())
                  .arg(response[5].c_str())
                  .arg(response[6].c_str());
    }
    
    QMessageBox::information(this, "My Responses", details);
}

void DonorRequestsBoard::onCloseClicked() {
    accept();
}

void DonorRequestsBoard::onTableCellDoubleClicked(int row, int column) {
    Q_UNUSED(column);
    int requestID = ui->tableBloodRequests->item(row, 0)->text().toInt();
    auto details = BloodRequest::getRequestDetails(*db, requestID);
    
    if (!details.empty()) {
        QString message = QString("Request ID: %1\nHospital: %2\nContact: %3\nBlood Type: %4\nUrgency: %5\nDate: %6")
                         .arg(details[0].c_str())
                         .arg(details[1].c_str())
                         .arg(details[2].c_str())
                         .arg(details[3].c_str())
                         .arg(details[4].c_str())
                         .arg(details[5].c_str());
        
        QMessageBox::information(this, "Request Details", message);
    }
}

// UPDATED FUNCTION - Filter requests by donor's blood group
void DonorRequestsBoard::loadAllRequests() {
    if (donorBloodGroup.isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Error", "Your blood group is not set. Please contact admin.");
        return;
    }
    
    // NEW - Use getRequestsByBloodType to filter by donor's blood group only
    auto requests = BloodRequest::getRequestsByBloodType(*db, donorBloodGroup.toStdString());
    
    if (requests.empty()) {
        ui->tableBloodRequests->setRowCount(0);
        QMessageBox::information(this, "No Requests", 
            QString("No blood requests found for your blood type (%1).\n\nWhen hospitals need %1 blood, requests will appear here.")
            .arg(donorBloodGroup));
    } else {
        displayRequests(requests);
    }
}

void DonorRequestsBoard::displayRequests(const std::vector<std::vector<std::string>>& requests) {
    ui->tableBloodRequests->setRowCount(0);
    
    for (size_t i = 0; i < requests.size(); ++i) {
        ui->tableBloodRequests->insertRow(i);
        
        for (size_t j = 0; j < requests[i].size(); ++j) {
            QTableWidgetItem *item = new QTableWidgetItem(QString::fromStdString(requests[i][j]));
            
            // NEW - Highlight matching blood type in green
            if (j == 3) { // Blood Type column
                item->setBackground(QColor(200, 255, 200)); // Light green
                item->setForeground(QColor(0, 100, 0)); // Dark green text
                QFont font = item->font();
                font.setBold(true);
                item->setFont(font);
            }
            
            ui->tableBloodRequests->setItem(i, j, item);
        }
    }
}

bool DonorRequestsBoard::isDonorEligible() {
    return DonationRequest::isDonorEligibleToDonate(*db, currentDonorID);
}
```

25] GUIManager.cpp
```
#include "GUIManager.h"
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int GUIManager::displayMainMenu() {
    int choice;
    cout << "\n===== BLOOD LIFE MENU =====\n";
    cout << "1. Register as Donor\n";
    cout << "2. Admin - Approve Donor\n";
    cout << "3. Hospital - Search Donors (in-memory)\n";
    cout << "4. Hospital - Save Last Search to Log\n";
    cout << "5. Hospital - View Search History\n";
    cout << "6. Analytics - Demand by Blood Group\n";
    cout << "7. Analytics - Area-wise Trends\n";
    cout << "8. Exit\n";
    cout << "Enter choice: ";
    cin >> choice;
    cin.ignore();
    return choice;
}

void GUIManager::showRows(const vector<vector<string>>& rows,
                          const vector<string>& headers) {
    if (!headers.empty()) {
        for (auto& h : headers) cout << h << "\t";
        cout << "\n";
    }
    if (rows.empty()) { cout << "(no rows)\n"; return; }
    for (auto& r : rows) {
        for (auto& c : r) cout << c << "\t";
        cout << "\n";
    }
}
```

26] Hospital.cpp
```
#include "Hospital.h"
#include <iostream>

using namespace std;

void Hospital::findDonors(DatabaseManager& db, string bloodGroup, string city) {
    string query = "SELECT name, phone, city, bloodGroup FROM Donor WHERE bloodGroup = '" + bloodGroup +
                   "' AND city = '" + city + "' AND approvalStatus = 1 AND available = 1";
    
    auto results = db.fetchResults(query);
    
    cout << "\n--- Available Donors ---\n";
    for (auto& row : results) {
        for (auto& col : row)
            cout << col << " ";
        cout << endl;
    }
    
    if (results.empty())
        cout << "No donors found.\n";
}
```

```
        "}"

        "   background: #8B3FF5;"

        "}"

        "   background: #333333;"  // ‚úÖ Match dialog background

        "}"
```
