        "   border-radius: 6px;"
        "}"
        "QScrollBar::handle:vertical {"
        "   background: #8B3FF5;"
        "   border-radius: 6px;"
        "   min-height: 30px;"
        "}"
        "QScrollBar::handle:vertical:hover {"
        "   background: #6B1FD5;"
        "}"
        "QScrollBar::add-line:vertical, QScrollBar::sub-line:vertical {"
        "   height: 0px;"
        "}"
        
        // ‚úÖ CALENDAR WIDGET STYLING
        "QCalendarWidget {"
        "   background: #2a2a2a;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QWidget {"
        "   background: #2a2a2a;"
        "   color: #FFFFFF;"  // ‚úÖ White text
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QToolButton {"
        "   background: #2a2a2a;"
        "   color: #FFFFFF;"  // ‚úÖ White text
        "   border: none;"
        "   padding: 8px;"
        "   font-size: 14px;"
        "   border-radius: 4px;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QToolButton:hover {"
        "   background: #3d3d3d;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QToolButton::menu-indicator {"
        "   image: none;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QMenu {"
        "   background: #2a2a2a;"
        "   color: #FFFFFF;"  // ‚úÖ White text
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QSpinBox {"
        "   background: #323131ff;"
        "   color: #FFFFFF;"  // ‚úÖ White text
        "   border: 1px solid #616060ff;"
        "   padding: 5px;"
        "   selection-background-color: #8B3FF5;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QWidget#qt_calendar_navigationbar {"
        "   background: #8B3FF5;"
        "   padding: 5px;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QWidget#qt_calendar_prevmonth,"
        "QCalendarWidget QWidget#qt_calendar_nextmonth {"
        "   background: transparent;"
        "   color: white;"
        "   border: none;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QAbstractItemView:enabled {"
        "   background: #2a2a2a;"
        "   color: #FFFFFF;"  // ‚úÖ White text for dates
        "   selection-background-color: #8B3FF5;"
        "   selection-color: white;"
        "   border: none;"
        "   outline: none;"
        "   font-size: 14px;"
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QAbstractItemView:disabled {"
        "   color: #666666;"  // ‚úÖ Gray for disabled dates
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QTableView {"
        "   background: #2a2a2a;"
        "   color: #FFFFFF;"  // ‚úÖ White date numbers
        "}"
        "QCalendarWidget QHeaderView::section {"
        "   background: #8B3FF5;"
        "   color: white;"
        "   padding: 5px;"
        "   border: none;"
        "   font-weight: bold;"
        "   font-size: 12px;"
        "}"
    );
    
    // Initially show login page
    ui->stackedWidget->setCurrentIndex(0);
    
    // ‚úÖ Setup combo boxes as NON-EDITABLE
    ui->cmbRegBloodGroup->addItems({"A+", "A-", "B+", "B-", "AB+", "AB-", "O+", "O-"});
    ui->cmbRegBloodGroup->setEditable(false);
    ui->cmbRegBloodGroup->setCurrentIndex(0);
    
    ui->cmbRegGender->addItems({"Male", "Female", "Other"});
    ui->cmbRegGender->setEditable(false);
    ui->cmbRegGender->setCurrentIndex(0);
    
    // Connect signals
    connect(ui->btnLogin, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &LoginDialog::onLoginClicked);
    connect(ui->btnRegister, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &LoginDialog::onRegisterClicked);
    connect(ui->lblSwitchToRegister, &QLabel::linkActivated, this, &LoginDialog::onSwitchToRegister);
    connect(ui->lblSwitchToLogin, &QLabel::linkActivated, this, &LoginDialog::onSwitchToLogin);
    connect(ui->btnBrowseHealthReport, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &LoginDialog::onBrowseHealthReportClicked);
}

LoginDialog::~LoginDialog() {
    delete ui;
}

void LoginDialog::onBrowseHealthReportClicked() {
    QString fileName = QFileDialog::getOpenFileName(this,
        "Select Health Report",
        QDir::homePath(),
        "Documents (*.pdf *.doc *.docx *.jpg *.jpeg *.png);;All Files (*)");
    
    if (!fileName.isEmpty()) {
        healthReportFilePath = fileName;
        QFileInfo fileInfo(fileName);
        ui->lblHealthReportStatus->setText(QString("‚úÖ Selected: %1").arg(fileInfo.fileName()));
        ui->lblHealthReportStatus->setStyleSheet("color: #1ABC9C; font-weight: bold;");
    }
}

bool LoginDialog::validateLoginInputs() {
    if (ui->txtLoginUsername->text().trimmed().isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter username/phone.");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (ui->txtLoginPassword->text().isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter password.");
        return false;
    }
    
    return true;
}

bool LoginDialog::validateRegisterInputs() {
    if (ui->txtRegName->text().trimmed().isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter your name.");
        return false;
    }
    
    QString phone = ui->txtRegPhone->text().trimmed();
    if (phone.length() != 10 || !phone.toULongLong()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter a valid 10-digit phone number.");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (ui->txtRegPassword->text().length() < 6) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Password must be at least 6 characters.");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (ui->txtRegPassword->text() != ui->txtRegConfirmPassword->text()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Passwords do not match.");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (ui->spinRegAge->value() < 18 || ui->spinRegAge->value() > 65) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Donor age must be between 18 and 65.");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (ui->txtRegCity->text().trimmed().isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter your city.");
        return false;
    }
    
    if (healthReportFilePath.isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error",
            "Please upload your health report document.");
        return false;
    }
    
    return true;
}

bool LoginDialog::authenticateAdmin(const QString& user, const QString& pass) {
    QString query = QString("SELECT adminID, adminName, password FROM Admin WHERE username = '%1' AND isActive = 1")
        .arg(user);
    auto results = db->fetchResults(query.toStdString());
    
    if (results.empty()) {
        return false;
    }
    
    if (results[0][2] == pass.toStdString()) {
        userID = std::stoi(results[0][0]);
        username = QString::fromStdString(results[0][1]);
        userType = ADMIN;
        return true;
    }
    
    return false;
}

bool LoginDialog::authenticateDonor(const QString& phone, const QString& pass) {
    QString query = QString("SELECT donorID, name, password FROM Donor WHERE phone = '%1' AND approvalStatus = 1")
        .arg(phone);
    auto results = db->fetchResults(query.toStdString());
    
    if (results.empty()) {
        return false;
    }
    
    if (results[0][2] == pass.toStdString()) {
        userID = std::stoi(results[0][0]);
        username = QString::fromStdString(results[0][1]);
        userType = DONOR;
        return true;
    }
    
    return false;
}

bool LoginDialog::registerDonor() {
    QString name = ui->txtRegName->text().trimmed();
    int age = ui->spinRegAge->value();
    QString gender = ui->cmbRegGender->currentText();
    QString phone = ui->txtRegPhone->text().trimmed();
    QString email = ui->txtRegEmail->text().trimmed();
    QString city = ui->txtRegCity->text().trimmed();
    QString address = ui->txtRegAddress->toPlainText().trimmed();
    QString bloodGroup = ui->cmbRegBloodGroup->currentText();
    QString password = ui->txtRegPassword->text();
    QString lastDonationDate = ui->dateRegLastDonation->date().toString("yyyy-MM-dd");
    
    // Check if phone already exists
    QString checkQuery = QString("SELECT phone FROM Donor WHERE phone = '%1'").arg(phone);
    auto existing = db->fetchResults(checkQuery.toStdString());
    if (!existing.empty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Registration Failed", "Phone number already registered!");
        return false;
    }
    
    // Copy health report to application folder
    QString appDataPath = QDir::currentPath() + "/health_reports";
    QDir dir;
    if (!dir.exists(appDataPath)) {
        dir.mkpath(appDataPath);
    }
    
    QFileInfo fileInfo(healthReportFilePath);
    QString newFileName = QString("%1_%2").arg(phone).arg(fileInfo.fileName());
    QString destinationPath = appDataPath + "/" + newFileName;
    if (QFile::exists(destinationPath)) {
        QFile::remove(destinationPath);
    }
    
    if (!QFile::copy(healthReportFilePath, destinationPath)) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "File Error", "Failed to save health report. Please try again.");
        return false;
    }
    
    // Insert new donor with health report path
    QString query = QString(
        "INSERT INTO Donor(name, age, gender, phone, email, city, address, bloodGroup, "
        "available, healthTestStatus, eligibilityStatus, approvalStatus, password, lastDonationDate, healthReportPath) "
        "VALUES('%1', %2, '%3', '%4', '%5', '%6', '%7', '%8', 0, 1, %9, 0, '%10', '%11', '%12')")
        .arg(name).arg(age).arg(gender).arg(phone).arg(email)
        .arg(city).arg(address).arg(bloodGroup)
        .arg((age >= 18 && age <= 65) ? 1 : 0)
        .arg(password)
        .arg(lastDonationDate)
        .arg(destinationPath);
    
    if (db->executeQuery(query.toStdString())) {
        QMessageBox::information(this, "Success",
            "‚úÖ Registration successful!\n\n"
            "üìÑ Health report uploaded\n"
            "üìÖ Last donation date recorded\n\n"
            "Your account is pending admin approval.\n"
            "You will be able to login once approved.");
        return true;
    } else {
        QMessageBox::critical(this, "Error", "Registration failed. Please try again.");
        return false;
    }
}

void LoginDialog::onLoginClicked() {
    if (!validateLoginInputs()) {
        return;
    }
    
    QString userInput = ui->txtLoginUsername->text().trimmed();
    QString password = ui->txtLoginPassword->text();
    
    if (authenticateAdmin(userInput, password)) {
        QMessageBox::information(this, "Login Success",
            QString("Welcome Admin: %1").arg(username));
        accept();
        return;
    }
    
    if (authenticateDonor(userInput, password)) {
        QMessageBox::information(this, "Login Success",
            QString("Welcome %1!").arg(username));
        accept();
        return;
    }
    
    QMessageBox::warning(this, "Login Failed",
        "Invalid credentials or account not approved.\n\n"
        "Donors: Use your phone number as username.\n"
        "Admin: Use your username.");
}

void LoginDialog::onRegisterClicked() {
    if (!validateRegisterInputs()) {
        return;
    }
    
    if (registerDonor()) {
        ui->stackedWidget->setCurrentIndex(0);
        ui->txtLoginUsername->clear();
        ui->txtLoginPassword->clear();
        healthReportFilePath.clear();
        ui->lblHealthReportStatus->setText("‚ùå No file selected");
        ui->lblHealthReportStatus->setStyleSheet("color: #E74C3C;");
    }
}

void LoginDialog::onSwitchToRegister() {
    ui->stackedWidget->setCurrentIndex(1);
    ui->txtRegName->clear();
    ui->txtRegPhone->clear();
    ui->txtRegEmail->clear();
    ui->txtRegCity->clear();
    ui->txtRegAddress->clear();
    ui->txtRegPassword->clear();
    ui->txtRegConfirmPassword->clear();
    ui->spinRegAge->setValue(25);
    healthReportFilePath.clear();
    ui->lblHealthReportStatus->setText("‚ùå No file selected");
    ui->lblHealthReportStatus->setStyleSheet("color: #E74C3C;");
}

void LoginDialog::onSwitchToLogin() {
    ui->stackedWidget->setCurrentIndex(0);
    ui->txtLoginUsername->clear();
    ui->txtLoginPassword->clear();
}
```

29] LoginDialog.ui
```
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<ui version="4.0">
 <class>LoginDialog</class>
 <widget class="QDialog" name="LoginDialog">
  <property name="geometry">
   <rect>
    <x>0</x>
    <y>0</y>
    <width>500</width>
    <height>700</height>
   </rect>
  </property>
  <property name="windowTitle">
   <string>Blood Life - Login</string>
  </property>
  <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="verticalLayout">
   <item>
    <widget class="QStackedWidget" name="stackedWidget">
     <property name="currentIndex">
      <number>0</number>

30] MainWindow.cpp
```
#include "MainWindow.h"
#include "ui_MainWindow.h"
#include "DonorDialog.h"
#include "AdminDialog.h"
#include "SearchDialog.h"
#include "AnalyticsDialog.h"
#include "DonorDashboard.h"
#include "BloodRequestDialog.h"
#include "DonorRequestsBoard.h"
#include "SearchLog.h"
#include <QMessageBox>
#include <QApplication>

MainWindow::MainWindow(QWidget *parent)
    : QDialog(parent)
    , ui(new Ui::MainWindow)
    , currentUserType(LoginDialog::NONE)
    , currentUserID(-1) {
    
    ui->setupUi(this);
    setWindowTitle("Blood Life Management System");
    setModal(true);
    resize(900, 700);

    // ‚úÖ CLEAN WHITE THEME - MATCHING LOGIN DIALOG

    db = new DatabaseManager();
    if (!db->connectDB()) {
        QMessageBox::critical(this, "Database Error",
            "Failed to connect to database.\n\n"
            "Please ensure:\n"
            "1. MySQL server is running\n"
            "2. Database 'blood_life_db' exists\n"
            "3. Check database credentials\n\n"
            "Application will exit.");
        reject();
        return;
    }
    
    setupConnections();
    updateUIForUserType();
}

MainWindow::~MainWindow() {
    db->closeConnection();
    delete db;
    delete ui;
}

void MainWindow::setLoggedInUser(LoginDialog::UserType type, int userID, const QString& username) {
    currentUserType = type;
    currentUserID = userID;
    currentUsername = username;
    
    QString userTypeStr = (type == LoginDialog::ADMIN) ? "Admin" : "Donor";
    ui->lblSubtitle->setText(QString("Welcome, %1 (%2)").arg(username).arg(userTypeStr));
    
    updateUIForUserType();
}

void MainWindow::setupConnections() {
    connect(ui->btnRegisterDonor, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &MainWindow::onRegisterDonorClicked);
    connect(ui->btnAdminApprove, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &MainWindow::onAdminApproveClicked);
    connect(ui->btnSearchDonors, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &MainWindow::onSearchDonorsClicked);
    connect(ui->btnViewSearchHistory, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &MainWindow::onViewSearchHistoryClicked);
    connect(ui->btnAnalytics, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &MainWindow::onAnalyticsClicked);
    connect(ui->btnDonorDashboard, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &MainWindow::onDonorDashboardClicked);
    connect(ui->btnBloodRequests, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &MainWindow::onBloodRequestsClicked);
    connect(ui->btnDonationBoard, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &MainWindow::onDonationBoardClicked);
    connect(ui->btnLogout, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &MainWindow::onLogoutClicked);
    connect(ui->btnExit, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &MainWindow::onExitClicked);
}

void MainWindow::updateUIForUserType() {
    if (currentUserType == LoginDialog::ADMIN) {
        ui->btnRegisterDonor->setVisible(true);
        ui->btnAdminApprove->setVisible(true);
        ui->btnSearchDonors->setVisible(true);
        ui->btnViewSearchHistory->setVisible(true);
        ui->btnAnalytics->setVisible(true);
        ui->btnBloodRequests->setVisible(true);
        ui->btnDonorDashboard->setVisible(false);
        ui->btnDonationBoard->setVisible(false);
    } else if (currentUserType == LoginDialog::DONOR) {
        ui->btnRegisterDonor->setVisible(false);
        ui->btnAdminApprove->setVisible(false);
        ui->btnSearchDonors->setVisible(false);
        ui->btnViewSearchHistory->setVisible(false);
        ui->btnAnalytics->setVisible(false);
        ui->btnBloodRequests->setVisible(false);
        ui->btnDonorDashboard->setVisible(true);
        ui->btnDonationBoard->setVisible(true);
    }
}

void MainWindow::onRegisterDonorClicked() {
    DonorDialog dialog(db, this);
    dialog.exec();
}

void MainWindow::onAdminApproveClicked() {
    AdminDialog dialog(db, this);
    dialog.exec();
}

void MainWindow::onSearchDonorsClicked() {
    SearchDialog dialog(db, this);
    dialog.exec();
}

void MainWindow::onViewSearchHistoryClicked() {
    auto history = SearchLog::getSearchHistory(*db, 1);
    if (history.empty()) {
        QMessageBox::information(this, "No History", "No search history found!");
        return;
    }
    
    QString historyText = "Search History:\n\n";
    for (const auto& entry : history) {
        historyText += QString("Blood Group: %1 | Area: %2 | Date: %3\n")
                      .arg(entry[1].c_str())
                      .arg(entry[2].c_str())
                      .arg(entry[3].c_str());
    }
    
    QMessageBox::information(this, "Search History", historyText);
}

void MainWindow::onAnalyticsClicked() {
    AnalyticsDialog dialog(db, this);
    dialog.exec();
}

void MainWindow::onDonorDashboardClicked() {
    if (currentUserType == LoginDialog::DONOR) {
        DonorDashboard dashboard(db, currentUserID, currentUsername, this);
        dashboard.exec();
    }
}

void MainWindow::onBloodRequestsClicked() {
    if (currentUserType == LoginDialog::ADMIN) {
        BloodRequestDialog dialog(db, this);
        dialog.exec();
    }
}

void MainWindow::onDonationBoardClicked() {
    if (currentUserType == LoginDialog::DONOR) {
        DonorRequestsBoard board(db, currentUserID, currentUsername, this);
        board.exec();
    }
}

void MainWindow::onLogoutClicked() {
    QMessageBox::StandardButton reply = QMessageBox::question(this, "Logout", 
                                                              "Are you sure you want to logout?",
                                                              QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
    
    if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
        reject();
    }
}

void MainWindow::onExitClicked() {
    QMessageBox::StandardButton reply = QMessageBox::question(this, "Exit", 
                                                              "Are you sure you want to exit the application?",
                                                              QMessageBox::Yes | QMessageBox::No);
    
    if (reply == QMessageBox::Yes) {
        accept();
    }
}

33] Search.cpp
```
#include "Search.h"
#include <iostream>

using namespace std;

// Executes donor search and holds data temporarily
int Search::executeSearch(DatabaseManager& db, const string& bg, const string& cty) {
    bloodGroup = bg;
    city = cty;
    results.clear();
    
    string query = "SELECT name, phone, city, bloodGroup FROM Donor "
                   "WHERE bloodGroup = '" + bg + "' "
                   "AND city = '" + cty + "' "
                   "AND approvalStatus = 1 AND available = 1";
    
    results = db.fetchResults(query);
    resultCount = static_cast<int>(results.size());
    
    cout << "\nüîç Search completed! " << resultCount << " donor(s) found.\n";
    for (auto& row : results) {
        for (auto& col : row)
            cout << col << "\t";
        cout << endl;
    }
    
    return resultCount;
}

// Clears all temporary memory data
void Search::clearMemory() {
    results.clear();
    resultCount = 0;
    bloodGroup.clear();
    city.clear();
    cout << "üßπ Temporary search data cleared from memory.\n";
}
```

34] SearchDialog.cpp
```
#include "SearchDialog.h"
#include "ui_SearchDialog.h"

SearchDialog::SearchDialog(DatabaseManager *database, QWidget *parent) :
    QDialog(parent),
    ui(new Ui::SearchDialog),
    db(database)
{
    ui->setupUi(this);
    setWindowTitle("Search Donors");
    resize(900, 600);
    
    // Setup blood group combo box
    ui->cmbBloodGroup->addItems({"A+", "A-", "B+", "B-", "AB+", "AB-", "O+", "O-"});
    
    // Setup table
    ui->tableResults->setColumnCount(4);
    ui->tableResults->setHorizontalHeaderLabels({"Name", "Phone", "City", "Blood Group"});
    ui->tableResults->horizontalHeader()->setStretchLastSection(true);
    ui->tableResults->setEditTriggers(QAbstractItemView::NoEditTriggers);
    ui->tableResults->setSelectionBehavior(QAbstractItemView::SelectRows);
    ui->tableResults->setSelectionMode(QAbstractItemView::SingleSelection);
    
    // Initially disable save button
    ui->btnSaveLog->setEnabled(false);
    
    connect(ui->btnSearch, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &SearchDialog::onSearchClicked);
    connect(ui->btnSaveLog, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &SearchDialog::onSaveLogClicked);
    connect(ui->btnClose, &QPushButton::clicked, this, &SearchDialog::onCloseClicked);
}

SearchDialog::~SearchDialog()
{
    delete ui;
}

void SearchDialog::onSearchClicked()
{
    QString bloodGroup = ui->cmbBloodGroup->currentText();
    QString city = ui->txtCity->text().trimmed();
    
    if (city.isEmpty()) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "Validation Error", "Please enter a city name.");
        return;
    }
    
    int count = search.executeSearch(*db, bloodGroup.toStdString(), city.toStdString());
    
    if (count > 0) {
        displayResults(search.getResults());
        ui->lblStatus->setText(QString("‚úÖ Found %1 donor(s)").arg(count));
        ui->btnSaveLog->setEnabled(true);
    } else {
        ui->tableResults->setRowCount(0);
        ui->lblStatus->setText("‚ùå No donors found matching the criteria.");
        ui->btnSaveLog->setEnabled(false);
    }
}

void SearchDialog::displayResults(const std::vector<std::vector<std::string>>& results)
{
    ui->tableResults->setRowCount(results.size());
    
    for (size_t i = 0; i < results.size(); ++i) {
        for (size_t j = 0; j < results[i].size() && j < 4; ++j) {
            QTableWidgetItem *item = new QTableWidgetItem(QString::fromStdString(results[i][j]));
            item->setTextAlignment(Qt::AlignCenter);
            ui->tableResults->setItem(i, j, item);
        }
    }
    
    // Resize columns to content
    ui->tableResults->resizeColumnsToContents();
}

void SearchDialog::onSaveLogClicked()
{
    if (search.getResultCount() == 0) {
        QMessageBox::warning(this, "No Search Data", 
                           "Please perform a search first before saving the log.");
        return;
    }
    
    // Save search log (hospitalID = 1 for demo purposes)
    bool saved = SearchLog::logSearch(*db, 1, search.getBloodGroup(), search.getCity());
    
    if (saved) {
        QMessageBox::information(this, "Success", 
                               "Search log saved successfully to database!");
        ui->btnSaveLog->setEnabled(false);
    } else {
        QMessageBox::critical(this, "Error", 
                            "Failed to save search log. Please try again.");
    }
}

void SearchDialog::onCloseClicked()
{
    accept();
}
```

37] SearchLog.cpp
```
#include "SearchLog.h"
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

// Save search details to DB
bool SearchLog::logSearch(DatabaseManager& db, int hospitalID, const string& bloodGroup, const string& area) {
    string query = "INSERT INTO SearchLog(hospitalID, bloodGroup, area, searchDate) VALUES(" +
                   to_string(hospitalID) + ", '" + bloodGroup + "', '" + area + "', CURRENT_DATE)";

    if (db.executeQuery(query)) {
        cout << "‚úÖ Search successfully logged in database.\n";
        return true;
    } else {
        cout << "‚ùå Failed to log search.\n";
        return false;
    }
}

// Retrieve search history for a hospital
vector<vector<string>> SearchLog::getSearchHistory(DatabaseManager& db, int hospitalID) {
    string query = "SELECT logID, bloodGroup, area, searchDate FROM SearchLog WHERE hospitalID = " +
                   to_string(hospitalID) + " ORDER BY searchDate DESC";

    return db.fetchResults(query);
}
```

38] main.cpp
```
#include "MainWindow.h"
#include "LoginDialog.h"
#include <QApplication>

int main(int argc, char *argv[])
{
    QApplication app(argc, argv);
    app.setStyle("Fusion");

    DatabaseManager db;
    if (!db.connectDB()) {
        return -1;
    }

    // FIXED: Logout loop - keeps showing login until exit
    while (true) {
        LoginDialog loginDialog(&db);
        
        if (loginDialog.exec() == QDialog::Accepted) {
            // Login successful, show main window
            MainWindow window;
            window.setLoggedInUser(
                loginDialog.getUserType(),
                loginDialog.getUserID(),
                loginDialog.getUsername()
            );
            
            // If window is closed, return to login
            // If app is quit (Exit button), break the loop
            int result = window.exec();
            
            if (result == QDialog::Rejected) {
                // User logged out, continue loop (show login again)
                continue;
            } else {
                // User clicked Exit, break loop and quit
                break;
            }
        } else {
            // Login cancelled, exit application
            break;
        }
    }
    
    return 0;
}
```

17] Search.h
```
#ifndef SEARCH_H
#define SEARCH_H

#include "DatabaseManager.h"
#include <string>
#include <vector>

class Search {
private:
    std::string bloodGroup;
    std::string city;
    std::vector<std::vector<std::string>> results;
    int resultCount = 0;

public:
    // Executes donor search (fetches from DB, stores in memory)
    int executeSearch(DatabaseManager& db, const std::string& bloodGroup, const std::string& city);
    
    // Clears temporary results from memory
    void clearMemory();
    
    // Getters
    const std::vector<std::vector<std::string>>& getResults() const { return results; }
    int getResultCount() const { return resultCount; }
    const std::string& getBloodGroup() const { return bloodGroup; }
    const std::string& getCity() const { return city; }
};

#endif // SEARCH_H
```

- Other files:-
1] bloodLife.pro
```
QT       += core gui widgets

greaterThan(QT_MAJOR_VERSION, 4): QT += widgets

CONFIG += c++17

# MySQL Configuration
win32 {
    INCLUDEPATH += "C:/Program Files/MySQL/MySQL Server 8.0/include"
    LIBS += -L"C:/Program Files/MySQL/MySQL Server 8.0/lib" -lmysql
    
    MYSQL_LIB = "C:/Program Files/MySQL/MySQL Server 8.0/lib"
    
    QMAKE_POST_LINK += $$quote(cmd /c copy /y \"$$MYSQL_LIB/libmysql.dll\" \"$$OUT_PWD/debug\"$$escape_expand(\n\t))
    QMAKE_POST_LINK += $$quote(cmd /c copy /y \"$$MYSQL_LIB/libssl-3-x64.dll\" \"$$OUT_PWD/debug\"$$escape_expand(\n\t))
    QMAKE_POST_LINK += $$quote(cmd /c copy /y \"$$MYSQL_LIB/libcrypto-3-x64.dll\" \"$$OUT_PWD/debug\"$$escape_expand(\n\t))
}

TARGET = BloodLife
TEMPLATE = app

DEFINES += QT_DEPRECATED_WARNINGS

SOURCES += \
    src/main.cpp \
    src/MainWindow.cpp \
    src/DonorDialog.cpp \
    src/SearchDialog.cpp \
    src/AdminDialog.cpp \
    src/AnalyticsDialog.cpp \
    src/LoginDialog.cpp \
    src/DonorDashboard.cpp \
    src/DatabaseManager.cpp \
    src/Admin.cpp \
    src/Analytics.cpp \
    src/Donor.cpp \
    src/Hospital.cpp \
    src/Search.cpp \
    src/SearchLog.cpp \
    src/GUIManager.cpp \
    src/BloodRequest.cpp \
    src/DonationRequest.cpp \
    src/BloodRequestDialog.cpp \
    src/DonorRequestsBoard.cpp

HEADERS += \
    include/MainWindow.h \
    include/DonorDialog.h \
    include/SearchDialog.h \
    include/AdminDialog.h \
    include/AnalyticsDialog.h \
    include/LoginDialog.h \
    include/DonorDashboard.h \
    include/DatabaseManager.h \
    include/Admin.h \
    include/Analytics.h \
    include/Donor.h \
    include/Hospital.h \
    include/Search.h \
    include/SearchLog.h \
    include/GUIManager.h \
    include/BloodRequest.h \
    include/DonationRequest.h \
    include/BloodRequestDialog.h \
    include/DonorRequestsBoard.h

FORMS += \
    src/MainWindow.ui \
    src/DonorDialog.ui \
    src/SearchDialog.ui \
    src/AdminDialog.ui \
    src/AnalyticsDialog.ui \
    src/LoginDialog.ui \
    src/DonorDashboard.ui \
    src/BloodRequestDialog.ui \
    src/DonorRequestsBoard.ui

INCLUDEPATH += include

# Default rules for deployment.
qnx: target.path = /tmp/$${TARGET}/bin
else: unix:!android: target.path = /opt/$${TARGET}/bin
!isEmpty(target.path): INSTALLS += target
```

2] copy_dll.bat
```
@echo off
setlocal

echo Copying required DLLs...

set MYSQL_LIB=C:\Program Files\MySQL\MySQL Server 8.0\lib
set BUILD_DIR=

REM Find the build directory
for /d %%D in (build-*) do (
    if exist "%%D\debug\BloodLife.exe" (
        set BUILD_DIR=%%D\debug
        goto found
    )
)

:found
if "%BUILD_DIR%"=="" (
    echo ERROR: Build directory not found!
    pause
    exit /b 1
)

echo Found build directory: %BUILD_DIR%
echo.

echo Copying DLLs...
copy "%MYSQL_LIB%\libmysql.dll" "%BUILD_DIR%\" /Y >nul
copy "%MYSQL_LIB%\libssl-3-x64.dll" "%BUILD_DIR%\" /Y >nul
copy "%MYSQL_LIB%\libcrypto-3-x64.dll" "%BUILD_DIR%\" /Y >nul

echo.
echo Done! All DLLs copied.
echo You can now run: %BUILD_DIR%\BloodLife.exe
pause
```

3] database_setup.sql
```
-- ============================================
-- BLOOD LIFE MANAGEMENT SYSTEM
-- FINAL FIXED VERSION - Run this complete file
-- ============================================

-- Drop and recreate for clean state
DROP DATABASE IF EXISTS blood;
CREATE DATABASE blood;
USE blood;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 1: Donor
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE Donor (
    donorID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    age INT NOT NULL,
    gender ENUM('Male', 'Female', 'Other') NOT NULL,
    phone VARCHAR(15) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    city VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    address TEXT NOT NULL,
    bloodGroup ENUM('A+', 'A-', 'B+', 'B-', 'AB+', 'AB-', 'O+', 'O-') NOT NULL,
    available BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    healthTestStatus BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    eligibilityStatus BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    approvalStatus BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    lastDonationDate DATE,
    registrationDate TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_bloodGroup (bloodGroup),
    INDEX idx_city (city),
    INDEX idx_approval (approvalStatus, available)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 2: Hospital
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE Hospital (
    hospitalID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    hospitalName VARCHAR(150) NOT NULL,
    address TEXT NOT NULL,
    city VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    state VARCHAR(50),
    pincode VARCHAR(10),
    contactNumber VARCHAR(15) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    licenseNumber VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    registrationDate TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    isActive BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE,
    INDEX idx_city (city)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 3: Admin (FIXED STRUCTURE)
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE Admin (
    adminID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    adminName VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    username VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    password VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    role ENUM('Super Admin', 'Admin', 'Moderator') DEFAULT 'Admin',
    createdDate TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    lastLogin TIMESTAMP NULL,
    isActive BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 4: SearchLog
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE SearchLog (
    logID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    hospitalID INT NOT NULL,
    bloodGroup ENUM('A+', 'A-', 'B+', 'B-', 'AB+', 'AB-', 'O+', 'O-') NOT NULL,
    area VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    searchDate DATE NOT NULL,
    searchTime TIME DEFAULT NULL,
    resultCount INT DEFAULT 0,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_hospitalID (hospitalID),
    INDEX idx_bloodGroup (bloodGroup),
    INDEX idx_searchDate (searchDate)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 5: DonationHistory
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE DonationHistory (
    donationID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    donorID INT NOT NULL,
    hospitalID INT NOT NULL,
    donationDate DATE NOT NULL,
    bloodGroup ENUM('A+', 'A-', 'B+', 'B-', 'AB+', 'AB-', 'O+', 'O-') NOT NULL,
    quantityML INT NOT NULL,
    donorHealthStatus ENUM('Excellent', 'Good', 'Fair') DEFAULT 'Good',
    notes TEXT,
    verifiedBy INT,
    createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_donorID (donorID),
    INDEX idx_hospitalID (hospitalID),
    INDEX idx_donationDate (donationDate)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 6: BloodRequest
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE BloodRequest (
    requestID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    hospitalID INT NOT NULL,
    patientName VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    patientAge INT NOT NULL,
    bloodGroup ENUM('A+', 'A-', 'B+', 'B-', 'AB+', 'AB-', 'O+', 'O-') NOT NULL,
    quantityRequired INT NOT NULL,
    urgency ENUM('Critical', 'Urgent', 'Normal') DEFAULT 'Normal',
    requestDate DATE NOT NULL,
    requiredBy DATE,
    status ENUM('Pending', 'Fulfilled', 'Cancelled') DEFAULT 'Pending',
    notes TEXT,
    createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_hospitalID (hospitalID),
    INDEX idx_status (status),
    INDEX idx_bloodGroup (bloodGroup)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 7: BloodInventory
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE BloodInventory (
    inventoryID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    bloodGroup ENUM('A+', 'A-', 'B+', 'B-', 'AB+', 'AB-', 'O+', 'O-') NOT NULL,
    quantityML INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
    location VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    expiryDate DATE NOT NULL,
    collectionDate DATE NOT NULL,
    donorID INT,
    status ENUM('Available', 'Reserved', 'Expired', 'Used') DEFAULT 'Available',
    lastUpdated TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_bloodGroup (bloodGroup),
    INDEX idx_status (status),
    INDEX idx_expiryDate (expiryDate)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 8: Notification
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE Notification (
    notificationID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    recipientType ENUM('Donor', 'Hospital', 'Admin') NOT NULL,
    recipientID INT NOT NULL,
    title VARCHAR(150) NOT NULL,
    message TEXT NOT NULL,
    notificationType ENUM('Urgent', 'Info', 'Reminder', 'Alert') DEFAULT 'Info',
    isRead BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_recipient (recipientType, recipientID),
    INDEX idx_isRead (isRead)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 9: AuditLog
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE AuditLog (
    logID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    userType ENUM('Admin', 'Hospital', 'Donor') NOT NULL,
    userID INT NOT NULL,
    action VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    tableName VARCHAR(50),
    recordID INT,
    description TEXT,
    ipAddress VARCHAR(45),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_userType (userType, userID),
    INDEX idx_timestamp (timestamp)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 10: EmergencyContact
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE EmergencyContact (
    contactID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    donorID INT NOT NULL,
    contactName VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    relationship VARCHAR(50),
    phoneNumber VARCHAR(15) NOT NULL,
    isPrimary BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    INDEX idx_donorID (donorID)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- INSERT SAMPLE DATA
-- ============================================

4] new.sql
```
-- ============================================
-- BLOOD LIFE MANAGEMENT SYSTEM
-- UPDATED VERSION WITH BLOOD REQUEST MANAGEMENT & 90-DAY COOLDOWN
-- ============================================

-- Drop and recreate for clean state
DROP DATABASE IF EXISTS blood;
CREATE DATABASE blood;
USE blood;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 1: Donor (UPDATED - Added healthReportPath & lastDonationDate index)
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE Donor (
    donorID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    age INT NOT NULL,
    gender ENUM('Male', 'Female', 'Other') NOT NULL,
    phone VARCHAR(15) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    city VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    address TEXT NOT NULL,
    bloodGroup ENUM('A+', 'A-', 'B+', 'B-', 'AB+', 'AB-', 'O+', 'O-') NOT NULL,
    available BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    healthTestStatus BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    eligibilityStatus BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    approvalStatus BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    lastDonationDate DATE,
    healthReportPath VARCHAR(255),
    registrationDate TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_bloodGroup (bloodGroup),
    INDEX idx_city (city),
    INDEX idx_approval (approvalStatus, available),
    INDEX idx_lastDonationDate (lastDonationDate)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 2: Hospital
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE Hospital (
    hospitalID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    hospitalName VARCHAR(150) NOT NULL,
    address TEXT NOT NULL,
    city VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    state VARCHAR(50),
    pincode VARCHAR(10),
    contactNumber VARCHAR(15) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    licenseNumber VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    registrationDate TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    isActive BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE,
    INDEX idx_city (city)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 3: Admin
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE Admin (
    adminID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    adminName VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    username VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    password VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    role ENUM('Super Admin', 'Admin', 'Moderator') DEFAULT 'Admin',
    createdDate TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    lastLogin TIMESTAMP NULL,
    isActive BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 4: SearchLog
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE SearchLog (
    logID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    hospitalID INT NOT NULL,
    bloodGroup ENUM('A+', 'A-', 'B+', 'B-', 'AB+', 'AB-', 'O+', 'O-') NOT NULL,
    area VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    searchDate DATE NOT NULL,
    searchTime TIME DEFAULT NULL,
    resultCount INT DEFAULT 0,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_hospitalID (hospitalID),
    INDEX idx_bloodGroup (bloodGroup),
    INDEX idx_searchDate (searchDate)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 5: DonationHistory
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE DonationHistory (
    donationID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    donorID INT NOT NULL,
    hospitalID INT NOT NULL,
    donationDate DATE NOT NULL,
    bloodGroup ENUM('A+', 'A-', 'B+', 'B-', 'AB+', 'AB-', 'O+', 'O-') NOT NULL,
    quantityML INT NOT NULL,
    donorHealthStatus ENUM('Excellent', 'Good', 'Fair') DEFAULT 'Good',
    notes TEXT,
    verifiedBy INT,
    createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_donorID (donorID),
    INDEX idx_hospitalID (hospitalID),
    INDEX idx_donationDate (donationDate)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 6: BloodRequest (MODIFIED FOR NEW FEATURE)
-- Changed from patient-specific to general donation request
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE BloodRequest (
    requestID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    hospitalID INT NOT NULL,
    hospitalName VARCHAR(150) NOT NULL,
    contactInfo VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    bloodGroup ENUM('A+', 'A-', 'B+', 'B-', 'AB+', 'AB-', 'O+', 'O-') NOT NULL,
    urgency ENUM('Critical', 'Urgent', 'Normal') DEFAULT 'Normal',
    requestDate DATE NOT NULL,
    status ENUM('Pending', 'Fulfilled', 'Cancelled') DEFAULT 'Pending',
    notes TEXT,
    createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_hospitalID (hospitalID),
    INDEX idx_status (status),
    INDEX idx_bloodGroup (bloodGroup),
    INDEX idx_requestDate (requestDate),
    FOREIGN KEY (hospitalID) REFERENCES Hospital(hospitalID) ON DELETE CASCADE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 7: DonationResponse (NEW - For 90-day cooldown feature)
-- Tracks donor responses to blood requests
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE DonationResponse (
    responseID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    donorID INT NOT NULL,
    requestID INT NOT NULL,
    status ENUM('Pending', 'Accepted', 'Rejected', 'Completed', 'Cancelled') DEFAULT 'Pending',
    responseDate DATE NOT NULL,
    createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_donorID (donorID),
    INDEX idx_requestID (requestID),
    INDEX idx_status (status),
    FOREIGN KEY (donorID) REFERENCES Donor(donorID) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    FOREIGN KEY (requestID) REFERENCES BloodRequest(requestID) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    UNIQUE KEY unique_response (donorID, requestID)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 8: BloodInventory
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE BloodInventory (
    inventoryID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    bloodGroup ENUM('A+', 'A-', 'B+', 'B-', 'AB+', 'AB-', 'O+', 'O-') NOT NULL,
    quantityML INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
    location VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    expiryDate DATE NOT NULL,
    collectionDate DATE NOT NULL,
    donorID INT,
    status ENUM('Available', 'Reserved', 'Expired', 'Used') DEFAULT 'Available',
    lastUpdated TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_bloodGroup (bloodGroup),
    INDEX idx_status (status),
    INDEX idx_expiryDate (expiryDate)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 9: Notification
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE Notification (
    notificationID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    recipientType ENUM('Donor', 'Hospital', 'Admin') NOT NULL,
    recipientID INT NOT NULL,
    title VARCHAR(150) NOT NULL,
    message TEXT NOT NULL,
    notificationType ENUM('Urgent', 'Info', 'Reminder', 'Alert') DEFAULT 'Info',
    isRead BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_recipient (recipientType, recipientID),
    INDEX idx_isRead (isRead)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 10: AuditLog
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE AuditLog (
    logID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    userType ENUM('Admin', 'Hospital', 'Donor') NOT NULL,
    userID INT NOT NULL,
    action VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    tableName VARCHAR(50),
    recordID INT,
    description TEXT,
    ipAddress VARCHAR(45),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX idx_userType (userType, userID),
    INDEX idx_timestamp (timestamp)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- ============================================
-- TABLE 11: EmergencyContact
-- ============================================
CREATE TABLE EmergencyContact (
    contactID INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    donorID INT NOT NULL,
    contactName VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    relationship VARCHAR(50),
    phoneNumber VARCHAR(15) NOT NULL,
    isPrimary BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
    INDEX idx_donorID (donorID)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

-- INSERT SAMPLE DATA
-- ============================================

(1, 1, 'Pending', CURDATE()),
(2, 2, 'Pending', CURDATE()),

-- ============================================
-- VERIFICATION & STATISTICS
-- ============================================

SELECT '=== DATABASE SETUP COMPLETE ===' AS Status;
SELECT CONCAT('Database: ', DATABASE()) AS CurrentDatabase;

SELECT '=== ALL TABLES CREATED ===' AS Status;
SHOW TABLES;

SELECT '=== ADMIN ACCOUNTS ===' AS Status;
SELECT adminID, adminName, username, email, role FROM Admin;

SELECT '=== HOSPITALS ===' AS Status;
SELECT hospitalID, hospitalName, city, contactNumber FROM Hospital;

SELECT '=== DONOR STATISTICS ===' AS Status;
SELECT 
    COUNT(*) AS TotalDonors,
    SUM(approvalStatus = 1) AS ApprovedDonors,
    SUM(approvalStatus = 0) AS PendingApproval,
    SUM(available = 1 AND approvalStatus = 1) AS AvailableDonors
FROM Donor;

SELECT '=== BLOOD REQUESTS ===' AS Status;
SELECT 
    COUNT(*) AS TotalRequests,
    SUM(status = 'Pending') AS PendingRequests,
    SUM(urgency = 'Critical') AS CriticalRequests
FROM BloodRequest;

SELECT '=== DONATION RESPONSES ===' AS Status;
SELECT 
    COUNT(*) AS TotalResponses,
    SUM(status = 'Pending') AS PendingResponses,
    SUM(status = 'Accepted') AS AcceptedResponses
FROM DonationResponse;

 ALTER TABLE Donor 
 ADD COLUMN password VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'donor123' AFTER approvalStatus;

SELECT '=== DONOR ELIGIBILITY (90-DAY COOLDOWN) ===' AS Status;
SELECT 
    name,
    bloodGroup,
    lastDonationDate,
    CASE 
        WHEN lastDonationDate IS NULL THEN 'Eligible - Never Donated'
        WHEN DATEDIFF(CURDATE(), lastDonationDate) >= 90 THEN CONCAT('Eligible - ', DATEDIFF(CURDATE(), lastDonationDate), ' days since last donation')
        ELSE CONCAT('Not Eligible - ', 90 - DATEDIFF(CURDATE(), lastDonationDate), ' days remaining')
    END AS EligibilityStatus
FROM Donor 
WHERE approvalStatus = 1
ORDER BY lastDonationDate DESC;

SELECT '=== SETUP SUCCESSFUL ===' AS Status;
SELECT 'You can now run your Qt application!' AS Message;
```
